WEBVTT

02:32.318 --> 02:34.112
Nhuan and Nhu, wake up!

02:35.864 --> 02:36.948
That's your alarm.

02:41.494 --> 02:42.620
Get up!

02:45.373 --> 02:47.250
- Mom!
- I'm up!

02:47.667 --> 02:49.169
I did it myself.

02:57.343 --> 02:58.428
Damn you Nhuan!

02:58.428 --> 02:59.637
Your fart stinks!

03:00.889 --> 03:02.724
- Everything you do is annoying.
- Nhuan!

03:02.932 --> 03:04.309
Pay me back the 10 bucks.

03:04.334 --> 03:05.878
After I poop.

03:05.903 --> 03:08.697
Flush it thoroughly or you'll know
how your life goes if it stinks.

03:09.856 --> 03:11.819
- Good morning grandma.
- Hello!

03:24.287 --> 03:25.413
Get up!

03:25.438 --> 03:27.752
- Get up!
- It's the weekend.

03:28.181 --> 03:29.970
Who says you can sleep in
on the weekend?

03:33.413 --> 03:34.706
How can a lady

03:35.033 --> 03:36.417
leave her toe nails like that?

03:36.800 --> 03:40.012
People would judge your family ethics
by these nails.

03:40.566 --> 03:43.780
A sloppy lady can't be a good one.

03:44.703 --> 03:45.746
Get up.

03:52.276 --> 03:53.733
- What the heck?
- Get up!

03:53.769 --> 03:55.571
I'm up! I'm up up up!

03:55.596 --> 03:57.347
- I'm up.
- Get up now.

03:57.946 --> 03:59.155
I'm up!

03:59.420 --> 04:01.203
I'm up!

04:07.072 --> 04:10.259
Why do you keep expanding your mess?

04:10.637 --> 04:12.097
How disgusting this is!

04:13.523 --> 04:16.651
Stop spending time on these
useless things.

04:16.676 --> 04:18.469
If you piss me off
I'll smash everything.

04:19.884 --> 04:21.719
Dress shirts stay with dress shirts.

04:22.345 --> 04:23.763
T-shirts stay with T-shirts.

04:23.930 --> 04:25.098
You have to separate them.

04:25.139 --> 04:27.433
But why? They're just clothes,
just mix them up.

04:27.458 --> 04:28.769
Do you eat rice mixed with bran,

04:28.794 --> 04:30.587
as they're from the same plant?

04:30.741 --> 04:32.237
Okay, you're the boss.

04:36.317 --> 04:38.569
You have to fold your underwear neatly.

04:38.594 --> 04:40.498
What for? Gotta spread them
to wear them anyway.

04:40.523 --> 04:41.441
Then spread when you do wear them.

04:41.466 --> 04:43.509
If you keep talking like that
I'll spread your face.

04:43.534 --> 04:46.078
Give me the receipt for the tuition.

04:46.103 --> 04:47.229
In the basket.

04:47.254 --> 04:49.664
- What basket?
- The hamper basket on the desk.

04:49.689 --> 04:51.732
- I threw it out.
- Why did you throw my stuff out?

04:51.757 --> 04:53.008
It looks ugly.

04:53.033 --> 04:56.244
It's ugly just to you. I put all my
receipts in there.

04:56.269 --> 04:59.316
Why would you put it there but
not your drawers?

04:59.341 --> 05:02.386
I can put it wherever I want.
Why did you have to throw it out?

05:02.442 --> 05:04.569
Stop explaining, just pick it up for me.

05:04.765 --> 05:05.891
Here's the receipt.

05:06.461 --> 05:07.400
Don't throw it out again.

05:07.425 --> 05:09.697
Do the same to me next time
so I won't ask.

05:11.201 --> 05:13.166
Where is all my stuff?

05:13.294 --> 05:14.784
I put them in the drawers.

05:15.804 --> 05:17.709
Why did you move them from the desk?

05:17.734 --> 05:20.213
What are the drawers for if you
keep putting things on the desk?

05:20.481 --> 05:23.088
I put them there for my convenience.

05:23.361 --> 05:25.446
Take things out from the drawers
when you need them.

05:25.471 --> 05:26.555
That's convenient too.

05:26.580 --> 05:28.916
Sure, you're the boss.

05:34.982 --> 05:36.275
What are you doing?

05:36.644 --> 05:38.479
That's what I wanna ask you.

05:39.103 --> 05:40.754
Why do you keep men in your room?

05:42.171 --> 05:43.422
What men?

05:43.447 --> 05:45.102
Those are photos.

05:45.282 --> 05:47.056
You think they're not "men" enough?

05:47.386 --> 05:49.009
What about when you're changing?

05:50.291 --> 05:51.834
Can't you see they're looking at you?

05:53.668 --> 05:55.838
No point in being grumpy.
Come and help me.

06:01.193 --> 06:02.236
Wow!

06:04.666 --> 06:05.959
Do not put lipstick on.

06:06.709 --> 06:08.419
I forgot to tell you.

06:12.206 --> 06:13.833
Hey sisters, come and join my stream.

06:13.858 --> 06:16.444
Just leave your phone number,
and give me a share.

06:16.469 --> 06:18.308
 I mean share my livestream,

06:18.333 --> 06:20.418
 what share do you think I was
talking about?

06:20.559 --> 06:21.602
 Thai cream!

06:21.627 --> 06:23.712
 It's all for your beauty.

06:23.737 --> 06:27.574
 Usually this jar costs 70 bucks,
but it's on sale for 7 bucks today.

06:28.648 --> 06:30.025
 Let me show you! See!

06:31.192 --> 06:33.069
 Delicious? I told you
it's all for your beauty,

06:33.094 --> 06:34.529
 this is not for business.

06:34.571 --> 06:35.780
 My whole family has extremely bright skin.

06:35.805 --> 06:38.103
 All the biatch from grandma to me.

06:38.805 --> 06:40.418
 Oops that was disrespectful!

06:46.633 --> 06:49.344
The texture of other sellers
are like sugarcane juice.

06:49.369 --> 06:51.494
Look at mine! Just like cream cheese!

06:51.519 --> 06:52.520
Nhuan!

06:52.545 --> 06:54.612
Nhuan, I need to borrow your arm.

06:55.175 --> 06:56.301
Nhuan!

06:58.011 --> 07:00.071
- What?
- Give me your arm.

07:00.096 --> 07:02.515
I have a tester for you guys.

07:02.540 --> 07:04.583
My husband! Hurry up!

07:04.608 --> 07:05.693
Your arm!

07:06.353 --> 07:07.354
Here, look at this.

07:07.395 --> 07:08.872
I'll test for you guys.

07:08.897 --> 07:12.152
Oh so so smooth! I put Gucci smell
in so it smells fantastic.

07:14.479 --> 07:15.647
Why does it stink?

07:15.672 --> 07:17.190
I've been cleaning the crabs.

07:18.883 --> 07:20.551
You're trying to sabotage me, aren't you?

07:21.409 --> 07:22.494
Your other arm.

07:24.204 --> 07:25.372
Here, have a look.

07:25.622 --> 07:28.333
This is the original ox-like skin tone.

07:28.358 --> 07:30.175
This is what my cream did to him.

07:30.200 --> 07:31.161
For real though!

07:31.186 --> 07:32.662
What more do you ask for?

07:32.687 --> 07:34.901
 He's normal, just looks a bit
ridiculous when he does this...

07:34.926 --> 07:35.940
 Oh for God's sake! Go away!

07:35.965 --> 07:37.008
Bye bye bye bye.

07:37.467 --> 07:38.802
 Chubby Piggy.

07:39.260 --> 07:41.054
 Don't yell at him, poor him.

07:41.137 --> 07:44.741
 Oh girl even that couldn't
get through to him.

07:44.766 --> 07:48.937
He only has to give his arms while I'm
streaming and he can't even do that.

07:48.962 --> 07:50.880
Live with my husband for a day, you'll see.

07:51.426 --> 07:52.510
Really though!

08:48.997 --> 08:51.124
Nhi are you up yet? Come give me a hand.

08:52.125 --> 08:53.460
Yes mom!

08:53.543 --> 08:55.336
Where are you?

08:55.420 --> 08:56.504
Right here!

08:56.723 --> 08:59.716
I woke you up to help me,
not for you to play with the ceramic.

08:59.741 --> 09:01.868
- What do you need?
- Peel the crabs.

09:01.893 --> 09:04.988
Peeling crab is way too mundane
for a university student.

09:05.013 --> 09:07.432
Does your degree make more money than I do?

09:07.599 --> 09:09.058
Why did you make me get it then?

09:09.142 --> 09:12.228
Well if you're too good for crab noodles
then go work at a bank. Stop talking back!

09:12.270 --> 09:13.746
Peel them and bring them downstairs.

09:13.771 --> 09:16.274
Nhuan, take the soup down for me.

09:16.299 --> 09:18.231
Nhuan, where are you?

09:20.945 --> 09:23.406
- Grab the deep-fried onion for me.
- Okay.

09:23.448 --> 09:25.909
Whatever you do, give her a hand,
or she'll yell at me again.

09:26.576 --> 09:27.844
Boiling soup!

09:28.703 --> 09:31.581
Guys, put some chopsticks on the tables.

09:31.808 --> 09:34.853
Hurry up, you guys are so slow.

09:35.376 --> 09:37.003
I don't get it!

09:50.600 --> 09:52.018
Boiling soup! Boiling soup!

09:52.352 --> 09:53.728
Watch out!

09:53.853 --> 09:56.664
Ladies and gentlement, 15 bucks for
a bowl of crab noodles.

09:56.689 --> 09:58.024
Can you believe that?

09:58.049 --> 10:00.239
It's the truth.

10:00.264 --> 10:04.380
I'm Le Minh Ho, and I'm standing at
Mrs. Nu's crab noodles restaurant,

10:04.405 --> 10:07.176
a very well-known place in Thu Duc area.

10:07.201 --> 10:08.468
The place is busy,

10:08.493 --> 10:09.911
and the owner is sassy.

10:09.936 --> 10:11.181
Don't want crab? Bye!

10:11.206 --> 10:12.520
Boiling soup everyone!

10:12.545 --> 10:15.298
Let's discover

10:15.542 --> 10:17.435
what makes these crabs

10:17.460 --> 10:20.255
as precious as crowns.

10:20.522 --> 10:23.191
Let's go inside!

10:23.216 --> 10:24.175
Come on!

10:24.217 --> 10:26.344
Get out of the way dude, what nonsense
are you talking about?

10:26.369 --> 10:28.429
I'm a Youtuber, I'm promoting
your restaurant.

10:28.471 --> 10:30.127
What is promoting? Line up if
you want food.

10:30.152 --> 10:31.653
I am lining up, there's my sandals.

10:32.642 --> 10:33.685
See?

10:34.352 --> 10:35.985
I'm serious with this.

10:36.190 --> 10:37.592
I know the rules well.

10:39.268 --> 10:41.221
Nhuan, go set up the tables.

10:43.152 --> 10:46.118
Okay, so I'm still not in yet.

10:46.148 --> 10:48.420
The sandals were not accepted.

10:48.493 --> 10:50.807
But it's fine. We'll start it over.

10:50.832 --> 10:53.293
- Should I put the aces here?
- Better move them down here.

10:53.318 --> 10:55.487
You have no ideas where
it should be put. Move.

10:55.512 --> 10:56.766
People come here for

10:56.791 --> 10:58.334
the taste of the crab noodles.

10:58.359 --> 10:59.686
The other part is for

10:59.711 --> 11:02.505
the taste of the owner's daughter.

11:02.630 --> 11:04.090
When I get inside...

11:04.090 --> 11:05.216
Hey hey hey!

11:05.258 --> 11:06.384
There she comes!

11:06.426 --> 11:07.427
Look at her!

11:17.203 --> 11:18.204
She's beautiful, isn't she?

11:18.229 --> 11:19.856
Great wife material!

11:30.575 --> 11:31.659
Are you okay?

11:31.743 --> 11:32.994
I'm so sorry.

11:33.119 --> 11:34.621
Can I take my crab back?

11:35.663 --> 11:36.664
What do you mean are you okay?

11:36.706 --> 11:38.699
- Don't you look at where you're going?
- I'm sorry.

11:38.724 --> 11:40.810
How can you throw a whole crab in her face?

11:40.835 --> 11:41.836
I'm sorry.

11:41.875 --> 11:44.347
- What's the matter?
- I dropped food on the customer.

11:44.372 --> 11:46.279
- Did you apologize?
- I did.

11:46.304 --> 11:49.027
Then why is he being so difficult?

11:49.052 --> 11:50.136
Oh my gosh!

11:50.136 --> 11:52.155
You staff dropped food on us,

11:52.180 --> 11:53.514
and you're having such an attitude?

11:53.539 --> 11:55.992
I got an earful before a mouthful.

11:56.017 --> 11:57.060
So annoying! Let's go!

11:57.060 --> 11:58.519
Go about your own business.

11:58.519 --> 12:02.857
She already apologized. It's not like
she meant to do it. Why so difficult?

12:02.882 --> 12:05.635
Your style of apologizing is more
like attacking.

12:05.693 --> 12:06.944
Why are you such an ass?

12:06.986 --> 12:09.947
She apologized politely,
what more do you want?

12:09.947 --> 12:11.324
What's with all the noises?

12:11.532 --> 12:12.867
Since you're here Liem,

12:13.034 --> 12:14.160
take care of this for me,

12:14.202 --> 12:16.079
they're disrupting public order.

12:16.120 --> 12:18.331
You're the one disrupting things.

12:18.456 --> 12:21.084
You gotta leave a pathway for people!

12:22.460 --> 12:23.503
Oh, sorry.

12:23.628 --> 12:25.254
Let's go! I'm so mad.

12:25.296 --> 12:28.049
We'll never ever come here again.

12:28.174 --> 12:29.676
It's fine sir.

12:29.717 --> 12:32.387
It's just two bowls, don't make it
a big deal.

12:32.387 --> 12:33.721
I believe I was polite.

12:33.721 --> 12:35.264
Mrs., please give me some thoughts.

12:35.306 --> 12:36.349
No thoughts asshole!

12:36.432 --> 12:37.767
- Go away!
- What?

12:51.280 --> 12:54.659
[March]

12:55.255 --> 12:56.352
When?

12:57.161 --> 13:00.157
I didn't deliver to the wrong address,
yet you still refused to pay.

13:00.182 --> 13:02.774
Now my husband have to open
all of them up.

13:03.006 --> 13:07.073
Life is difficult enough for me,
please be a polite buyer.

13:07.179 --> 13:09.649
Please pay for your orders, it's unethical
otherwise.

13:09.674 --> 13:11.249
When did you take that one?

13:11.274 --> 13:12.595
A while ago.

13:12.620 --> 13:13.663
Why didn't you tell me?

13:13.862 --> 13:15.029
I didn't know your cards.

13:15.054 --> 13:17.223
That's cheating, I don't wanna play
anymore.

13:17.390 --> 13:18.433
Don't be like that!

13:22.937 --> 13:24.188
I got a pimple!

13:24.397 --> 13:26.215
Should I go to your birthday party?

13:27.233 --> 13:28.593
But I'm so ugly, what do I do?

13:29.669 --> 13:31.713
Can you please stop scratching
while I'm streaming?

13:31.738 --> 13:32.739
It's itchy.

13:35.616 --> 13:37.285
I wasn't cheating.

13:37.285 --> 13:38.453
Nope!

13:38.453 --> 13:41.038
- It's dinner time mom.
- Yeah it's my dinner time.

13:41.080 --> 13:42.039
Finish the round.

13:42.039 --> 13:43.708
Nah, this household has dinner
at 7pm sharp.

13:43.750 --> 13:45.293
These are going on clearance sale.

13:45.334 --> 13:47.795
Please buy it for me.

13:47.820 --> 13:50.389
- Nhuan, come here.
- Are you guys done?

13:50.414 --> 13:52.260
Imma smash that phone.

13:52.285 --> 13:53.867
Go get the eggs for me.

13:56.012 --> 13:57.346
My mom is mad now.

13:57.346 --> 13:58.598
I gotta end the stream.

14:04.479 --> 14:05.480
Where did you get these?

14:05.938 --> 14:08.691
Nhi made them, she said they'd look good
for dinner.

14:08.775 --> 14:11.194
Good? Looks like we bought
second-hand bowls.

14:11.402 --> 14:12.987
Switch back to the white ones.

14:13.070 --> 14:14.113
Got it.

14:16.115 --> 14:17.283
I'm leaving now.

14:18.951 --> 14:20.495
Huh? Introduce me to who?

14:20.953 --> 14:22.789
Just wait til I get there.

14:22.789 --> 14:24.771
Leaving now. Hanging up. Bye.

14:25.416 --> 14:29.086
Call Nhi for dinner.
Why isn't she here yet?

14:29.111 --> 14:30.279
She's coming.

14:31.099 --> 14:32.726
Grandma, mom, I'm off to
a birthday party.

14:32.751 --> 14:34.107
Whose birthday is it today?

14:34.343 --> 14:36.343
My friend Lan.

14:36.402 --> 14:38.046
Why didn't you tell me
you're going?

14:38.071 --> 14:40.031
I did, I told you last week.

14:40.056 --> 14:41.974
You said I have to ask for permission
a week in advance.

14:41.974 --> 14:43.100
That was last week.

14:43.125 --> 14:44.919
You gotta remind me this week.

14:44.944 --> 14:46.139
How can I remember?

14:46.270 --> 14:47.313
So what now?

14:47.338 --> 14:49.123
Have dinner then go.

14:49.609 --> 14:51.526
Have dinner before going to a party?

14:51.551 --> 14:53.219
She'd be full before having anything.

14:54.570 --> 14:55.863
It's none of your business.

14:57.516 --> 14:58.642
Your boss is right. Just have dinner.

15:00.802 --> 15:03.429
Please enjoy your meal.

15:03.454 --> 15:05.164
Okay, you can eat first.

15:05.189 --> 15:06.341
Thank you.

15:06.496 --> 15:07.886
Don't fight it.

15:07.911 --> 15:10.311
No one can change the rules
in this household.

15:10.336 --> 15:13.144
Change your shirt after having dinner.

15:13.169 --> 15:16.032
It's a bit revealing on your chest.

15:17.343 --> 15:18.553
This is revealing?

15:18.808 --> 15:19.893
Can't you see?

15:39.365 --> 15:40.408
- Sorry.
- Oh?

15:40.449 --> 15:41.492
Oh, Quynh!

15:41.534 --> 15:43.244
Nhi! Lan's in here.

15:43.286 --> 15:44.287
- Lan's in here.
- Okay.

15:44.287 --> 15:46.831
Excuse me, excuse me.

15:47.164 --> 15:49.041
Lan! Lan! Nhi's here.

15:49.041 --> 15:50.126
Hey!

15:55.298 --> 15:56.424
Going to church?

15:56.632 --> 15:58.009
You look like a nun...

15:58.050 --> 15:59.677
Who makes the miracle I'm here.

15:59.702 --> 16:01.537
Happy birthday!

16:09.319 --> 16:10.320
Hey!

16:11.147 --> 16:12.899
What are you doing
in front of my house?

16:13.983 --> 16:15.067
I'm looking for you.

16:15.318 --> 16:16.319
Why?

16:16.736 --> 16:18.154
You were grumpy this morning.

16:18.779 --> 16:20.865
Here's some hot sweet soup
to cool you down.

16:21.032 --> 16:23.175
You think that makes sense?

16:23.200 --> 16:24.493
Green beans! They'll cool you down.

16:24.577 --> 16:25.995
Why do you keep giving me sweet soup?

16:26.020 --> 16:30.160
We're living in the same building,
figured I'd practice taking care of you.

16:31.070 --> 16:32.071
But hey...

16:32.096 --> 16:34.520
You gotta tidy up your
restaurant set up.

16:34.545 --> 16:37.757
People are complaining, it's hard for me
being in the middle.

16:38.174 --> 16:39.675
Your house is one floor,

16:39.717 --> 16:41.469
not the whole building.

16:41.636 --> 16:42.803
I got it.

16:42.828 --> 16:44.530
Stop giving me sweet soup though.

16:44.555 --> 16:45.932
- Why?
- People will talk.

16:45.957 --> 16:47.135
What's there to talk about?

16:47.160 --> 16:48.912
My sweet soup smells really nice.

16:48.937 --> 16:50.188
- Smell it!
- It stinks!

16:50.213 --> 16:51.983
- How can it be stinky?
- My garbage.

16:52.008 --> 16:54.898
- I was gonna take it out. Hang on!
- Nu!

16:56.014 --> 16:58.016
Take the sweet soup, I'll take the garbage.

16:58.041 --> 16:59.590
- But why?
- I'll take it out for you.

17:00.009 --> 17:01.218
Thank you.

17:03.074 --> 17:04.659
But hey, I mean...

17:06.077 --> 17:07.119
Too fast, too furious.

17:11.666 --> 17:13.000
How are you two still a couple?

17:13.042 --> 17:15.252
Six years, still happy.

17:15.628 --> 17:17.338
They keep saying I've broken up,

17:17.338 --> 17:19.507
but we're still in love
to spite them.

17:19.596 --> 17:21.389
I'd think you're the slutty kind.

17:22.557 --> 17:24.627
You're neither funny nor charmy.

17:26.027 --> 17:27.236
What's your secret?

17:28.270 --> 17:29.693
Don't underestimate him,

17:29.718 --> 17:31.577
we do it once everyday,

17:31.602 --> 17:34.084
three times on a good day,

17:34.511 --> 17:36.791
once every three days on a bad day,

17:36.816 --> 17:38.790
but never go without it!

17:39.536 --> 17:41.372
- Stop!
- Open your eyes!

17:41.673 --> 17:42.674
Be satisfied!

17:43.462 --> 17:44.940
Open your eyes and look!

17:45.653 --> 17:47.023
Enjoy it!

17:48.744 --> 17:50.641
I'm done. Go dance.

17:51.153 --> 17:53.274
Please excuse me.

17:57.128 --> 17:58.587
Why don't you go dance?

17:58.938 --> 18:00.481
It's my pleasure to dance with you.

18:00.506 --> 18:01.424
What for?

18:01.449 --> 18:02.702
Okay, I'll do it myself.

18:06.971 --> 18:09.207
Why did you invite him?

18:09.232 --> 18:11.600
He used to hit on me, now it's
embarrassing to meet him.

18:11.642 --> 18:14.600
Remember I said I'll introduce
you to someone?

18:14.871 --> 18:16.747
- Don't tell me it's him.
- No way.

18:16.772 --> 18:17.857
His friend.

18:17.882 --> 18:20.167
He didn't want to come alone,

18:20.192 --> 18:21.777
that's what I invite Quynh for.

18:21.802 --> 18:22.720
Who is it?

18:22.857 --> 18:24.980
Tall, football, the guy who has them all,

18:25.005 --> 18:27.758
my cousin, a struggling Viet Kieu
who just came back to Vietnam.

18:27.783 --> 18:29.577
Wow that sounds promising!

18:29.577 --> 18:31.642
Of course it is!

18:32.997 --> 18:35.182
Nhi! To the left!

18:35.207 --> 18:37.334
- What?
- To the left!

19:03.194 --> 19:05.529
Sorry John! I was dancing!

19:06.947 --> 19:08.032
Clumsy idiot!

19:09.533 --> 19:10.659
Happy birthday Lan!

19:11.285 --> 19:12.411
Thank you!

19:13.120 --> 19:14.828
Cheer up everyone!

19:15.284 --> 19:16.410
Let me introduce you to

19:16.496 --> 19:18.931
Nhi, my friend.

19:19.085 --> 19:21.212
Nhi, this is my cousin.

19:21.237 --> 19:22.501
Viet Kieu.

19:25.257 --> 19:26.884
Hello. I'm John.

19:27.218 --> 19:28.344
Hello.

19:36.769 --> 19:37.937
That hurts.

19:38.395 --> 19:39.438
Piss off.

19:39.730 --> 19:40.815
Get out of here!

19:41.899 --> 19:43.859
Your calves are stiff as tree logs.

19:44.068 --> 19:45.277
You scream when I go light,

19:45.694 --> 19:46.918
and yell when I go hard.

19:46.946 --> 19:48.447
No idea how to please you.

19:48.472 --> 19:49.681
Any problems?

20:01.710 --> 20:03.167
Working out grandma?

20:03.410 --> 20:05.448
You're sneaking out to drink, aren't you?

20:05.473 --> 20:06.515
Absolutely not.

20:07.057 --> 20:09.385
My wife's friend is pregnant.

20:09.410 --> 20:11.837
I mean, my friend's wife is pregnant.

20:11.887 --> 20:13.973
He asked me to come give a hand.

20:14.014 --> 20:15.391
Liar.

20:18.686 --> 20:20.688
I have 5 bucks here, you can
use it for gambling.

20:21.689 --> 20:23.892
Do not ever do this to me.

20:24.108 --> 20:25.860
- I'm sorry.
- Just this time.

20:26.986 --> 20:29.071
I mean men should drink with his friends.

20:29.405 --> 20:30.914
- Now you can go.
- Thank you.

20:37.454 --> 20:40.624
Undo your hair! Who would hit
on you if you wear braids?

20:40.666 --> 20:42.209
My mom will kill me.

20:42.251 --> 20:43.919
- Who gives a shit?
- What?

20:44.044 --> 20:45.617
I mean it's gonna be okay.

20:45.629 --> 20:47.339
You gotta lure this cool dude first.

20:47.381 --> 20:48.549
- No!
- Do it!

20:48.549 --> 20:50.509
No! No! No!

21:23.709 --> 21:25.699
They got hooked faster than I thought.

21:25.878 --> 21:27.510
That's normal.

21:27.595 --> 21:29.180
What a bitch!

21:29.205 --> 21:30.906
- Really?
- Just like me.

21:32.092 --> 21:33.289
Let's take a selfie!

21:34.136 --> 21:35.179
Kiss me!

22:28.691 --> 22:30.401
- I'm sorry.
- It's okay.

22:30.442 --> 22:31.694
But you were such a good dancer.

22:31.735 --> 22:33.487
I was just bouncing,
you're better.

22:33.487 --> 22:35.322
- I made the dances up.
- I like that.

22:35.322 --> 22:36.282
Really?

22:36.633 --> 22:38.416
What do you do for a living?

22:39.368 --> 22:41.355
- I'm a designer.
- Cool.

22:41.380 --> 22:43.123
- What about you?
- I'm an architect.

22:43.163 --> 22:44.823
Amazing!

22:46.166 --> 22:47.626
Can I get your phone number?

22:47.651 --> 22:49.840
- I don't think so.
- Why?

22:55.404 --> 22:56.906
Why didn't you pick up my calls?

22:56.934 --> 22:59.246
I left my phone in the purse,
didn't hear it.

22:59.596 --> 23:00.848
Did you consume alcohol?

23:01.122 --> 23:03.539
Just a little bit while being out
with friends.

23:03.659 --> 23:04.994
Have you asked me for permission?

23:05.019 --> 23:07.910
I did, just a sip for her birthday.

23:07.935 --> 23:09.270
You're a girl and you're drinking?

23:09.295 --> 23:11.172
Alcohol is just another drink,

23:11.197 --> 23:12.901
not as serious as you made it
out to be.

23:12.926 --> 23:15.090
So I gotta wait until she's
as drunk as you?

23:15.563 --> 23:18.190
You're her brother in law,
she's learning from you.

23:18.424 --> 23:19.817
That's nonsense mom.

23:19.842 --> 23:21.719
My husband is drunk on his own,

23:21.744 --> 23:23.861
and she just grew up to be naughty,

23:23.886 --> 23:25.929
- they're unrelated!
- Of course they're related.

23:26.033 --> 23:27.297
You're her sister.

23:27.322 --> 23:29.406
You're the idol she looks up to, no?

23:29.431 --> 23:30.936
- Hey, hey.
- You go against my will to marry

23:30.961 --> 23:33.380
- this loser who drinks all day.
- It's not your business, go home.

23:33.405 --> 23:34.682
- Yes, mr. Liem.
- Go home.

23:34.707 --> 23:36.155
- Is that not enough for you?
- Yes.

23:36.300 --> 23:37.634
- You're being unreasonable!
- Weirdo.

23:37.842 --> 23:38.780
- Unreasonable?
- And you too.

23:38.805 --> 23:41.181
- Now that you're making money,
- It's too late, go home and sleep.

23:41.206 --> 23:43.041
what you say is right.

23:43.066 --> 23:45.138
You'd go there? Fine, I lose.

23:45.163 --> 23:46.177
See that?

23:46.202 --> 23:47.745
She yells at me because of you.

23:47.770 --> 23:50.564
From now on you have to to tell me
where you're going.

23:50.606 --> 23:53.016
No more birthday parties.

23:53.041 --> 23:54.780
No more friends named Lan.

23:54.805 --> 23:57.046
Anyone with an L initial is forbidden.

23:57.071 --> 23:59.206
L stands for lusty.

23:59.231 --> 24:02.770
If this ever happens again
I'll kill myself.

24:03.339 --> 24:04.465
What?

24:05.108 --> 24:08.263
Can you lower your volume
when yelling at her?

24:08.288 --> 24:10.129
The neighbors are complaining,

24:10.154 --> 24:12.287
plus you gotta keep her face too.

24:12.419 --> 24:14.255
Got it. I'll speak softer.

24:18.258 --> 24:20.054
So "soft".

24:21.178 --> 24:22.767
Go to your room

24:23.305 --> 24:25.140
or stay here til she kills somebody?

24:25.258 --> 24:26.717
Move!

24:26.742 --> 24:28.202
Who would dare to kill your husband?

24:28.227 --> 24:29.620
He's the king.

24:29.645 --> 24:31.438
I'm not a king, I'm just...

24:31.438 --> 24:32.856
A bastard.

24:32.898 --> 24:37.194
People yelling, we keep silent.

24:37.219 --> 24:42.182
- When they're burning, we keep frozen.
- Shut up and go inside.

24:43.700 --> 24:46.053
Fart again? Damn you.

24:46.078 --> 24:47.373
Go to your room.

24:49.748 --> 24:51.668
You're throwing up too?

24:51.693 --> 24:54.208
You clean that up yourself,
I won't do it.

24:54.233 --> 24:55.698
Get the hell out of here.

24:56.510 --> 24:57.919
Damn you Nhuan!

25:06.640 --> 25:09.672
I made you some warm milk,
drink it then go to sleep.

25:10.936 --> 25:12.871
Don't do that again, okay?

25:12.896 --> 25:14.606
I know you don't like getting yelled at.

25:16.233 --> 25:17.902
Move your butt in.

25:17.927 --> 25:19.575
It's better for your spine.

25:20.279 --> 25:22.143
It's difficult to have daughters.

25:29.715 --> 25:31.976
[I had fun dancing with you]

25:33.568 --> 25:35.725
[Didn't think you're such a weirdo!]

25:37.671 --> 25:39.515
[Nice to know you.
Let's meet again some time.]

25:49.558 --> 25:50.684
Mom, what are you doing?

25:50.726 --> 25:52.227
Talking to your bae, aren't you?

25:52.311 --> 25:53.729
- No I'm not.
- Yes you are.

25:53.770 --> 25:55.105
You were in there for hours.

25:56.440 --> 25:57.566
No I'm not.

25:57.649 --> 25:58.970
You are.

25:58.995 --> 26:01.962
You've been dreamy ever since
you got back from the States.

26:01.987 --> 26:03.113
Put your love aside.

26:03.138 --> 26:05.757
Focus on work, help me manage
the factories.

26:05.782 --> 26:07.659
We have nothing but money.

26:07.684 --> 26:09.344
You can have all the wives you want.

26:09.369 --> 26:10.496
What did you say?

26:10.532 --> 26:12.967
I said he can have all the lives he wants.

26:12.992 --> 26:14.754
Okay? Help me please!

26:14.779 --> 26:16.084
Dad! What the heck!

26:19.296 --> 26:20.783
Why is he pooping again?

26:25.302 --> 26:26.653
Phu Nhuan.

26:26.678 --> 26:27.846
Nhi's brother in law.

26:27.846 --> 26:28.931
He's dull.

26:28.931 --> 26:31.341
Everyone just walks all over him.

26:32.726 --> 26:34.041
She's got a big mouth!

26:34.066 --> 26:36.199
Ngoc Nhu, whitening cream queen.

26:36.224 --> 26:38.142
She's making money so
she's got an attitude.

26:39.441 --> 26:40.442
Ngoc Nga.

26:40.484 --> 26:41.527
Grandma.

26:41.777 --> 26:44.488
I'm still working on her, not sure
which side of the spectrum she's on.

26:45.697 --> 26:46.698
And that!

26:47.407 --> 26:49.826
The final Boss you have to conquer.

26:49.868 --> 26:51.662
Ngoc Nhi's mom.

26:51.776 --> 26:53.487
Ngoc Nu!

26:55.874 --> 26:57.334
You know her family so well!

26:57.376 --> 26:59.912
Of course, I had a crush on Nhi.

26:59.937 --> 27:01.522
I stood no chance, so I'll let you.

27:01.547 --> 27:02.962
I did my research.

27:03.882 --> 27:05.968
- Thanks bud!
- Accepted!

27:06.338 --> 27:08.237
Either way, you stand no chance.

27:08.262 --> 27:09.513
Her mom is difficult!

27:09.555 --> 27:11.782
She's been so difficult and
full of hatred,

27:11.807 --> 27:13.367
ever since Nhu married Nhuan.

27:13.392 --> 27:14.560
You have no idea who she is.

27:16.996 --> 27:18.455
She was born difficult.

27:18.480 --> 27:19.731
That's just the way she is.

27:19.731 --> 27:20.886
Wait, who are you?

27:21.775 --> 27:23.026
Just a Youtuber.

27:23.026 --> 27:25.195
But I camp here long enough
to know every news.

27:25.404 --> 27:26.488
You really do?

27:26.513 --> 27:28.010
Like a family member.

27:28.232 --> 27:29.449
Let me tell you.

27:29.903 --> 27:32.344
Mrs. Nu's husband dumped her,

27:32.369 --> 27:34.371
so she hated men.

27:34.371 --> 27:36.248
She was strict then.

27:36.248 --> 27:38.250
Then Nhu got married,

27:38.292 --> 27:39.543
she got even stricter.

27:39.585 --> 27:41.670
Nhuan is really useless for a man,

27:41.670 --> 27:43.021
so dependent on his woman.

27:43.046 --> 27:44.923
And she hates him publicly.

27:45.299 --> 27:47.144
When Nhu married him,

27:47.169 --> 27:49.319
she fought with her mom
to the brink of disowning.

27:49.344 --> 27:51.431
They still have a rough relationship.

27:51.792 --> 27:54.626
Nhi is now her hope and pride.

27:54.651 --> 27:56.432
She cherishes her like a flower.

27:56.464 --> 27:59.304
So she watches her closely.
Any dude hitting on her, oh my...

27:59.346 --> 28:01.473
she'd drench him in her soup.

28:01.498 --> 28:03.542
She's got the mentality of a cheater hater,

28:03.567 --> 28:04.985
me against the whole wide world.

28:04.985 --> 28:07.304
Red Fairy Li Mochou.

28:20.292 --> 28:21.335
So?

28:22.210 --> 28:23.378
You still good?

28:23.545 --> 28:24.588
I'll handle it.

28:24.630 --> 28:26.247
You better handle yourself.

28:26.256 --> 28:27.733
Hey John John John!

28:27.758 --> 28:29.602
- To the left!
- What?

28:29.627 --> 28:31.358
To the left!

28:58.849 --> 29:00.738
Get a seat dude. Clear the way!

29:01.833 --> 29:03.591
Go get their orders!

29:03.616 --> 29:05.869
What are you looking at? Sit down.

29:06.661 --> 29:09.576
Did you see that? Did you see that?

29:09.758 --> 29:11.551
I said I can handle this.

29:11.635 --> 29:13.928
And I can see it. Good luck!

29:23.359 --> 29:24.229
Hey!

29:25.273 --> 29:26.618
Who are you guys looking at?

29:27.522 --> 29:29.607
Why are you soliciting?

29:30.445 --> 29:31.755
Is your crush in here?

29:31.780 --> 29:33.277
- Liar!
- You have a crush on me?

29:33.302 --> 29:34.636
Someone must have told you.

29:34.921 --> 29:37.174
Damn these young kids!

29:37.411 --> 29:39.454
Be careful Nhi, a lot of
dudes have eyes on you.

29:39.479 --> 29:41.427
Let me take this.

29:41.452 --> 29:42.745
You go give mom a hand.

29:43.679 --> 29:45.936
Be careful! They're dangerous!

29:45.961 --> 29:48.454
You are fearless.
Don't come here again.

29:48.505 --> 29:50.100
I'd die if someone find out.

29:50.978 --> 29:52.349
Talking to a dude?

29:52.426 --> 29:54.219
Yes ma'am, have a good night.

29:54.594 --> 29:56.627
I'll visit you.

29:57.848 --> 29:59.633
What dude? My teacher.

29:59.658 --> 30:01.264
Teacher or gangster?

30:01.309 --> 30:02.436
What?

30:02.468 --> 30:04.384
I can tell it in your eyes.

30:05.355 --> 30:06.690
Be careful.

30:07.566 --> 30:09.526
Your teacher is so handsome!

30:09.776 --> 30:11.503
Grandma!

30:11.528 --> 30:13.505
I'm old, you can't hide things from me.

30:13.530 --> 30:16.333
You were talking to the dude
that was at the restaurant, weren't you?

30:16.358 --> 30:18.068
I don't know him.

30:18.093 --> 30:19.845
Then why did he look at you?

30:19.870 --> 30:21.621
Who wouldn't look at me when I'm this cute?

30:21.646 --> 30:23.273
But why did you look at him?

30:25.876 --> 30:26.918
Huh?

30:27.031 --> 30:28.116
Answer me!

30:28.170 --> 30:29.528
It's nothing mom.

30:40.015 --> 30:41.057
Hello!

30:41.356 --> 30:42.409
What's up dude?

30:42.434 --> 30:44.286
- Is this Lan?
- Yes. Wait?

30:44.311 --> 30:46.551
I forbid you to hang out with my daughter.

30:46.576 --> 30:48.232
What kind of friend are you?

30:48.491 --> 30:51.811
You talked her into drinking,
then you introduced your cousin to her?

30:52.043 --> 30:54.103
Tell him to stay away from her.

30:54.128 --> 30:55.547
He's a douchebag.

30:55.572 --> 30:57.883
I know that just from his face.

30:57.908 --> 31:01.783
How dare he come to my house and
hit on her in front of me?

31:01.808 --> 31:03.138
Don't provoke me.

31:03.163 --> 31:06.196
Once I've decided, there's no turning back.

31:06.221 --> 31:07.601
Remember that!

31:07.626 --> 31:10.295
And you, you must ask for permission
everywhere you go.

31:10.320 --> 31:13.325
You will not go out alone ever again.
Stop crying!

31:24.142 --> 31:25.492
Here you go! Thank you.

31:25.517 --> 31:26.411
Okay.

31:26.436 --> 31:27.804
- Nhi!
- Yes?

31:28.605 --> 31:29.648
Smile.

31:31.191 --> 31:33.319
- What's that for?
- Report to your mom.

31:33.401 --> 31:34.444
Damn!

31:34.486 --> 31:37.187
Gotta abide by the rules,
or she'll kill me.

31:39.032 --> 31:40.951
- Brother!
- What? What do you want?

31:42.744 --> 31:43.870
Want a deal?

31:44.496 --> 31:46.723
Want a deal? Or want me to be killed?

31:46.748 --> 31:47.749
No.

31:47.791 --> 31:50.335
I mean let's help each other out.

31:53.713 --> 31:57.050
I know you're only drinking
to have some fun with your friends.

31:58.845 --> 32:01.492
But my sister seems to be
too harsh on you.

32:05.094 --> 32:07.906
Do you want someone
to open the door for you,

32:08.104 --> 32:09.564
every night when you come home?

32:17.571 --> 32:19.540
No, I don't.

32:20.923 --> 32:22.008
Thank you brother in law.

32:22.033 --> 32:23.496
No I'm not.

32:23.521 --> 32:25.189
Be back on time.

32:25.495 --> 32:26.821
Don't just leave.

32:29.708 --> 32:31.304
Thanh? Yeah!

32:31.636 --> 32:32.762
Wanna grab a drink tonight?

32:33.336 --> 32:35.088
Same place.

32:38.430 --> 32:40.093
How do you know I like these places?

32:40.171 --> 32:41.625
I'm John.

32:48.602 --> 32:51.411
Chubby Piggy, here's your cream.

33:01.948 --> 33:03.325
What an occasion!

33:03.366 --> 33:04.492
Cheers!

33:05.214 --> 33:06.338
- I gotta go.
- Okay.

33:06.363 --> 33:07.804
- Coffee?
- Following the protocol.

33:07.829 --> 33:09.289
Hang on! Wait a minute!

33:09.372 --> 33:11.625
Okay okay, it's coming.

33:11.625 --> 33:12.792
Two bowls!

33:12.817 --> 33:14.110
Less sweet next time, John.

33:14.135 --> 33:15.261
Okay brother.

33:16.254 --> 33:17.756
[I brought Nhi to skool!]

33:19.257 --> 33:21.804
- You got a table?
- Come on in.

33:22.052 --> 33:23.589
Go get their orders!

33:24.596 --> 33:25.889
Same place tonight.

33:28.934 --> 33:30.060
Grandma!

33:37.817 --> 33:40.545
I'll give you one incense stick time.
Don't just leave.

33:40.570 --> 33:41.696
Thank you grandma.

33:49.162 --> 33:50.205
Namo Amitabud.

33:50.764 --> 33:52.165
I'm here, I'm here.

33:52.190 --> 33:53.515
Traffic was crazy.

33:54.499 --> 33:56.436
- Your helmet!
- I forgot.

33:56.461 --> 33:57.754
My bad my bad!

33:57.796 --> 34:00.690
- We had fun because of you.
- Damn your fun!

34:00.715 --> 34:02.734
- Your happiness is my worriness.
- Bye bye.

34:02.759 --> 34:03.802
Bye brother in law!

34:03.802 --> 34:04.886
- Hello Nhi!
- Hi!

34:04.928 --> 34:06.596
- You're really pretty today!
- Thank you!

34:06.621 --> 34:08.123
- Hi Nhuan!
- Yes, go to work?

34:08.148 --> 34:08.999
I'm home, mom.

34:09.024 --> 34:11.416
- Get change then come over for fruits.
- Yes.

34:12.516 --> 34:14.412
- Ooh mango!
- Wait for grandma!

34:18.952 --> 34:20.620
We're in the international
trading business,

34:20.645 --> 34:22.267
yet you're dating a crab noodle girl.

34:22.396 --> 34:23.480
So foolish of you!

34:23.613 --> 34:25.080
What's wrong with that?

34:25.615 --> 34:26.815
I don't like that family.

34:27.033 --> 34:28.233
So rude!

34:28.827 --> 34:31.788
If you keep dating her
I'll mess everything up.

34:33.873 --> 34:35.326
Why did you cook crab noodle?

34:37.377 --> 34:38.503
Lost my appetite!

34:39.942 --> 34:40.985
He finished it though.

34:41.394 --> 34:42.562
Weirdo!

34:42.841 --> 34:44.319
Why did he take it out on me?

34:44.344 --> 34:45.735
- No clue.
- Let him be!

34:45.760 --> 34:46.970
I still like crab noodle.

34:48.847 --> 34:51.032
But I don't like your girl.

34:51.224 --> 34:52.809
Mom, listen to me.

34:52.809 --> 34:54.559
No need to talk, keep eating.

34:58.815 --> 35:00.358
So pretty!

35:00.859 --> 35:02.485
You know everything.

35:02.569 --> 35:03.647
I'm John.

35:04.237 --> 35:07.407
It's amazing that you found this kind
of place in the middle of Saigon.

35:07.907 --> 35:11.643
Just like I found you amongst the
7 billions people on this planet.

35:12.281 --> 35:13.574
So cheesy!

35:14.456 --> 35:16.207
Cheesy aside, don't you agree that,

35:16.249 --> 35:18.376
these are the things you were imagining?

35:18.376 --> 35:19.502
That's right.

35:20.211 --> 35:22.130
This might make me look bad...

35:22.589 --> 35:24.674
Give birth to me, my parents.

35:25.050 --> 35:27.385
Understand me, my John.

35:27.719 --> 35:28.970
Sorry, sorry.

35:32.724 --> 35:34.734
Wow they're amazing!

35:36.770 --> 35:38.586
Look at this!

35:39.230 --> 35:41.149
Where else in Saigon
can you find these things?

35:42.817 --> 35:44.586
If I have money,

35:44.611 --> 35:46.234
I'd open a place just like this.

35:46.259 --> 35:47.990
- Do you like it?
- Of course.

35:48.015 --> 35:50.625
Let's do it then. We'll do it together.

35:51.398 --> 35:52.525
You're crazy!

35:53.411 --> 35:55.096
You think I have that kind of money?

35:55.121 --> 35:57.229
No, I'm serious.

35:57.265 --> 35:58.641
How can you say you're serious?

35:58.666 --> 36:00.085
Do you need a slap to be waken up?

36:03.546 --> 36:04.631
I'm serious about

36:04.672 --> 36:07.884
planning to open a cafe like this,
with you.

36:08.885 --> 36:10.278
I know you like it too,

36:10.303 --> 36:11.346
don't you?

36:11.904 --> 36:13.865
For real? Stop joking around!

36:13.890 --> 36:14.974
I'm serious.

36:15.578 --> 36:17.175
- Thank you!
- Thank you.

36:17.435 --> 36:19.729
I studied architecture in the States,
you like pottery.

36:19.754 --> 36:21.214
We both like this style.

36:21.239 --> 36:22.657
If I ever told my parents,

36:22.690 --> 36:24.442
they would definitely say...

36:25.735 --> 36:27.076
- Cafe?
- Yeah.

36:27.101 --> 36:29.645
I think you should focus on
international trading.

36:29.830 --> 36:31.341
Ever since I met you,

36:31.366 --> 36:33.477
we both know the values of
these things, right?

36:33.502 --> 36:35.379
- Right.
- But our parents don't.

36:35.620 --> 36:36.704
Mom!

36:36.704 --> 36:38.957
I also think you should work in
international trading.

36:38.957 --> 36:40.583
Anything that the youth wants,

36:40.583 --> 36:42.794
the adults always view as nonsense.

36:42.919 --> 36:44.687
- Yep!
- But they don't know that,

36:44.712 --> 36:47.257
- they're not understanding us.
- Yes!

36:47.282 --> 36:48.366
See?

36:48.775 --> 36:50.026
I wish you were my mom!

36:50.051 --> 36:51.052
What?

36:51.052 --> 36:52.320
No, because...

36:52.345 --> 36:53.263
I mean...

36:53.263 --> 36:56.057
I wish my mom could understand me
like you do.

36:56.432 --> 36:59.102
Mom always looks down on
the things that I do.

37:02.772 --> 37:03.898
What is this?

37:04.232 --> 37:05.275
Orange juice.

37:05.300 --> 37:06.442
It goes for a dollar on the street,

37:06.480 --> 37:07.485
4 dollars here,

37:07.510 --> 37:08.719
and 8 dollars at the airport.

37:09.279 --> 37:12.478
The value of a thing lies on
where it was placed.

37:15.910 --> 37:16.953
I don't get it.

37:18.456 --> 37:22.210
I know your dreams are not silly at all.

37:22.500 --> 37:24.961
You just need a partner.

37:29.382 --> 37:31.259
We will open a cafe like this,

37:31.259 --> 37:33.261
without being dependent on anyone.

37:34.095 --> 37:35.604
And we will succeed.

37:36.890 --> 37:37.891
Trust me!

37:42.812 --> 37:43.980
Thank you John.

37:45.231 --> 37:48.109
[April]

37:51.806 --> 37:54.093
Nhuan! I need to borrow your arm!

37:55.925 --> 37:58.030
Here, just look at my texture,
then we'll talk.

38:02.498 --> 38:05.188
Just leave your phone number...

38:07.986 --> 38:11.660
- You lose, drink it, 100%.
- Okay, I'm loser.

38:17.388 --> 38:19.465
- Ooh that's good.
- Keep the whole thing.

38:19.552 --> 38:21.220
- It's really good.
- Keep it.

38:34.150 --> 38:35.433
Thanks brother.

38:37.450 --> 38:38.451
[June]

38:47.120 --> 38:48.544
Here's 5 bucks for you.

38:48.586 --> 38:51.057
I don't like this, but I'll take it.

38:51.082 --> 38:52.208
Thank you grandma.

38:52.233 --> 38:53.177
Cheers!

38:58.137 --> 39:00.531
You are the best.

39:00.819 --> 39:01.945
You can cook,

39:02.101 --> 39:03.186
you can make money,

39:03.211 --> 39:05.251
a great husband,
a good son-in-law,

39:05.276 --> 39:06.788
you're good at everything.

39:06.813 --> 39:09.274
Where can you find another you?

39:09.299 --> 39:11.306
What more does Nhu want from you?

39:11.768 --> 39:12.894
Isn't that right?

39:13.194 --> 39:14.279
Absolutely!

39:14.304 --> 39:15.472
She's so mean.

39:15.792 --> 39:17.377
She needs to know her place.

39:17.402 --> 39:18.403
Hey!

39:19.701 --> 39:20.785
Don't say that.

39:21.953 --> 39:23.329
You guys know me well.

39:24.956 --> 39:26.291
I wear the pants at home.

39:26.582 --> 39:28.376
Then how come she keep
forbidding you to go out?

39:29.043 --> 39:30.545
That's entirely up to me.

39:30.920 --> 39:33.481
Some times you need to
keep the order in your family,

39:33.506 --> 39:34.757
so you gotta make sacrifices.

39:34.874 --> 39:36.918
No one can stop me if
I wanna go.

39:37.802 --> 39:39.821
I can control my wife
with a snap, really.

39:39.846 --> 39:42.223
Let's drink to that snapping thing!

39:44.058 --> 39:46.185
Hang on, I forgot my phone
in the bathroom.

39:46.602 --> 39:48.396
- Looking for this?
- Oh thank you.

39:52.275 --> 39:54.085
How did you know?

39:54.110 --> 39:55.570
'Cause you left it at home.

39:58.364 --> 40:00.158
No, listen to us.

40:01.284 --> 40:02.577
Bastard! Asshole!

40:02.602 --> 40:04.687
Mom! Mom! Mom!

40:04.904 --> 40:06.031
- Mom!
- Bastard!

40:06.456 --> 40:07.768
I was right to hate you.

40:07.915 --> 40:09.796
I only ask you to do one thing,

40:09.821 --> 40:11.823
and you still manage to
disappoint me.

40:11.928 --> 40:13.554
She's young and dumb so
I'll let it go.

40:13.579 --> 40:14.872
But you're old enough,

40:14.897 --> 40:16.107
and still you aided her,

40:16.132 --> 40:17.783
pushing her to date that dude.

40:17.808 --> 40:19.769
Are you trying to harm this family?

40:19.794 --> 40:20.924
That's enough mom!

40:20.949 --> 40:22.780
Focus on the wrong doing here.

40:22.805 --> 40:26.034
Why are you saying he's harming us?
What has he done?

40:26.059 --> 40:27.477
He's corrupting your sister,

40:27.502 --> 40:29.629
- and you're picking his side?
- Shut up!

40:30.567 --> 40:31.831
Why did shut me up?

40:31.856 --> 40:33.324
I meant Nhu.

40:33.349 --> 40:36.019
Your husband is clearly in the wrong,
and you're on his side?

40:37.270 --> 40:38.396
Tell me.

40:38.913 --> 40:40.414
Why did you do things
behind my back?

40:43.034 --> 40:45.111
No, I mean, if I didn't help her,

40:45.136 --> 40:47.138
she can still sneak out to see him.

40:47.163 --> 40:48.247
Shut up!

40:48.348 --> 40:51.559
You have no right to talk right now.

40:51.584 --> 40:53.311
Are you trying to provoke her?

40:53.336 --> 40:54.562
I'm only saying the truth.

40:54.587 --> 40:56.372
Let me ask you. The kid seems okay,

40:56.397 --> 40:57.982
he's handsome, his family is nice,

40:58.007 --> 41:00.927
she's old enough to have a boyfriend,
why are you forbidding her?

41:00.968 --> 41:02.248
Who said you can talk?

41:02.273 --> 41:03.851
Are you trying to teach me?

41:03.971 --> 41:05.684
I'm not, but I think it's true.

41:05.709 --> 41:06.766
Shut up.

41:06.791 --> 41:09.714
- Grandma told you to shut up.
- I meant your mom.

41:09.831 --> 41:11.120
But why?

41:11.145 --> 41:12.688
I think Nhuan is right.

41:12.713 --> 41:14.916
The kid is handsome, just let her be.

41:14.941 --> 41:17.927
You're sabotaging what I'm
trying to teach her.

41:18.381 --> 41:19.466
Now!

41:19.491 --> 41:20.575
You!

41:20.600 --> 41:21.714
Tell me.

41:21.739 --> 41:23.591
Nhuan took you to school,

41:23.616 --> 41:25.660
then did you actually go to classes?

41:25.660 --> 41:27.274
You went out with him, didn't you?

41:28.204 --> 41:29.414
Speak!

41:33.770 --> 41:38.473
The show must go on...

41:38.506 --> 41:39.507
Hello.

41:39.549 --> 41:41.676
I'm actually in a family fight,
I'll call you back.

41:58.286 --> 42:00.080
Thank you ladies and gentlemen

42:00.105 --> 42:04.285
for coming to the grand opening of
our 7th factory.

42:06.826 --> 42:08.202
Starting today,

42:08.202 --> 42:11.581
my son will manage this factory
on behalf of the family.

42:11.622 --> 42:14.625
I hope you all can support him.

42:21.090 --> 42:23.801
Thank you all for being here this morning.

42:26.137 --> 42:27.388
You bastard!

42:29.390 --> 42:30.475
What the heck?

42:34.270 --> 42:36.063
What? Oh my! Oh my gosh!

42:36.564 --> 42:38.147
How handsome how rich you are!

42:38.608 --> 42:41.117
You're handsome enough to
impregnant my daughter?

42:41.611 --> 42:43.362
Mrs! Calm down!

42:43.404 --> 42:44.912
Calm down my ass!

42:45.183 --> 42:46.434
Let go of me!

42:46.459 --> 42:48.044
Why? Why?

42:48.409 --> 42:49.827
Why did you do that?

42:49.869 --> 42:52.184
- What is it?
- Why did you do that?

42:52.254 --> 42:53.589
How can you do that to my sister?

42:53.614 --> 42:55.033
How?

42:56.952 --> 42:58.686
- You bastard!
- Are you ok?

42:58.711 --> 43:01.153
- He made my daughter pregnant.
- He impregnated her.

43:01.178 --> 43:02.672
You're just an ass behind
a pretty cover.

43:02.697 --> 43:04.157
How could you betray my trust?

43:04.182 --> 43:05.808
You should watch your back!

43:06.344 --> 43:07.897
Be careful when you go out!

43:07.922 --> 43:09.808
This is not over yet.

43:10.068 --> 43:11.613
Bastard!

43:15.019 --> 43:17.580
Fortunately again I was here

43:17.605 --> 43:19.357
to send to you this significant news.

43:19.440 --> 43:21.125
Dai Phat's owner's son

43:21.150 --> 43:23.461
impregnated Mrs. Nu's daughter.

43:23.486 --> 43:24.654
Are you getting shocked?

43:24.695 --> 43:26.030
- Shoc...
- What's shocking?

43:26.055 --> 43:27.965
I'm reporting...

43:27.990 --> 43:30.394
Report what? What's the good news
to report?

43:30.868 --> 43:33.371
- No, please give me my tool back.
- Give you what?

43:33.412 --> 43:35.373
At least you warn me first,
you can't take my tools.

43:35.414 --> 43:37.250
You gotta know what you should
or shouldn't record.

43:37.275 --> 43:38.932
I'll learn. No, my phone!

43:45.132 --> 43:46.175
Look at this.

43:46.200 --> 43:47.450
It's all over the internet.

43:50.640 --> 43:51.974
Are you happy now?

43:52.619 --> 43:54.466
This kid made her pregnant.

43:55.048 --> 43:56.504
I've been working so hard

43:56.975 --> 43:57.976
through all these years

43:58.001 --> 44:00.408
to build my reputation, and now

44:00.760 --> 44:03.305
I get yelled at by a bitch

44:03.330 --> 44:04.786
in front of everyone.

44:04.831 --> 44:06.170
Are you happy now?

44:06.195 --> 44:08.535
- That was her mom, not her.
- Shut up!

44:10.408 --> 44:11.957
This is all your fault.

44:12.885 --> 44:15.012
If you didn't sleep with her
and give her a baby,

44:15.037 --> 44:18.124
she wouldn't have a chance
to scream in my face like that.

44:18.608 --> 44:20.402
Why are you dating such a low-life?

44:21.085 --> 44:22.128
Huh?

44:26.674 --> 44:27.758
Tomorrow,

44:28.426 --> 44:29.510
go back to the States.

44:29.535 --> 44:30.636
I don't want to.

44:30.678 --> 44:33.088
You have no stand to
negotiate with me.

44:34.432 --> 44:35.766
What should we do

44:35.808 --> 44:37.059
with the pregnant girl?

44:37.388 --> 44:38.556
I'll take the baby.

44:38.936 --> 44:41.622
Or give them money and they'll go away.

44:41.647 --> 44:43.316
That's all they're messing for.

44:43.341 --> 44:44.384
Dad!

44:45.187 --> 44:46.815
Don't say that about her family.

44:46.978 --> 44:48.150
Oh my!

44:48.175 --> 44:49.218
What?

44:50.192 --> 44:51.661
What are you gonna do?

44:52.450 --> 44:53.851
Hit me?

44:54.105 --> 44:55.189
Go ahead!

44:58.914 --> 45:00.299
Jerk.

45:04.474 --> 45:05.475
Thang.

45:05.999 --> 45:09.035
Book a ticket for John
to go back to LA.

45:09.060 --> 45:10.103
The earliest flight.

45:10.128 --> 45:11.410
Don't look at me like that.

45:11.729 --> 45:13.265
I won't take your side.

45:13.544 --> 45:14.957
You're so wrong.

45:15.733 --> 45:17.119
Do as your dad said.

45:17.320 --> 45:19.774
We'll handle her family.

45:39.525 --> 45:40.965
Why did you do this?

45:50.301 --> 45:51.993
How can you do this to me?

45:56.889 --> 45:58.281
What do you want?

46:04.908 --> 46:06.980
Please let me move out.

46:15.128 --> 46:17.092
Do I treat you that bad?

46:25.131 --> 46:26.215
Yes.

46:28.272 --> 46:30.999
- Very.
- What did I do?

46:33.899 --> 46:37.235
I've never been allowed to do
what I want in this family.

46:38.007 --> 46:40.626
Dating is obviously out of the question,

46:40.672 --> 46:43.316
but my career, my major,

46:43.613 --> 46:46.017
or my clothes,

46:46.254 --> 46:49.676
you even control me from keeping my nails.

46:50.940 --> 46:53.264
I'm like a doll in your hands.

46:53.289 --> 46:55.191
So you can do what ever you want to it.

46:56.782 --> 46:59.326
I'm living your dreams for you.

47:06.125 --> 47:09.370
I've never had you do anything.

47:12.527 --> 47:14.528
I asked you to help with the restaurant,

47:17.631 --> 47:20.385
so you can see how hard I work.

47:21.974 --> 47:23.184
So you could carry the torch.

47:25.012 --> 47:27.790
If you didn't like that then
go to the university.

47:27.815 --> 47:29.282
Be a banker.

47:30.010 --> 47:32.381
There are obviously
two ways for you to pick.

47:32.451 --> 47:34.313
Will potteries give you money?

47:35.242 --> 47:36.368
I told you to stop,

47:36.393 --> 47:38.363
you said I'm forbidding your career.

47:38.574 --> 47:40.593
Keep you from dating the douchebags,

47:40.618 --> 47:42.581
you said I'm interfering with your love.

47:43.120 --> 47:45.080
What exactly do you want me to do for you?

47:55.027 --> 47:57.641
I know you've done plenty for me.

48:01.855 --> 48:04.296
But why aren't you doing
the things I really need?

48:05.935 --> 48:07.311
What do you need?

48:07.336 --> 48:09.797
I need to live like a normal person.

48:10.851 --> 48:14.174
To do what I like,
to study what I want.

48:15.155 --> 48:17.984
I've never liked
Financial And Banking University

48:18.009 --> 48:19.573
even for a day.

48:20.950 --> 48:22.832
I did it for you.

48:24.286 --> 48:25.996
Why don't you let me pick?

48:26.330 --> 48:27.498
So I can fight for it,

48:27.498 --> 48:28.999
I might fail but that's okay,

48:29.041 --> 48:30.709
why are you protecting me?

48:35.589 --> 48:38.592
Every parents want their kids
to be successful.

48:39.969 --> 48:41.929
And you're forcing me to let you fail.

48:42.388 --> 48:43.848
What does that even mean?

48:45.140 --> 48:48.102
Because it's a human's right
to experience failure.

48:50.229 --> 48:52.648
I'd rather fail in my dream,

48:54.024 --> 48:56.439
than succeed in yours.

48:58.081 --> 48:59.082
Okay.

48:59.446 --> 49:00.614
You did it.

49:01.156 --> 49:02.908
I'm experiencing failure.

49:03.161 --> 49:06.706
Spent all those years raising you
and now you're pregnant out of wedlock.

49:07.496 --> 49:08.914
I failed!

49:12.167 --> 49:13.335
Why?

49:13.669 --> 49:15.921
Why did you do that?

49:16.338 --> 49:17.590
Tell me.

49:22.206 --> 49:24.208
Mom, calm down.

49:24.680 --> 49:25.931
Are you a mute now?

49:25.969 --> 49:27.846
I asked why did you do that?

49:28.496 --> 49:29.887
Because I wanted to.

49:34.236 --> 49:35.413
I want to move out.

49:36.006 --> 49:37.474
Then leave now.

49:38.553 --> 49:39.630
Leave!

49:42.137 --> 49:43.263
I'm sorry.

49:44.450 --> 49:45.534
Hey!

49:45.736 --> 49:47.595
Nhi! Apologize!

49:47.914 --> 49:49.115
Are you insane?

49:49.476 --> 49:50.477
Nhu!

49:50.502 --> 49:52.474
- Let her go.
- Mom!

49:52.499 --> 49:55.044
Anyone that tries to stop her
will be disowned.

49:55.069 --> 49:56.278
Let her go.

50:00.682 --> 50:02.092
Oh my gosh!

50:05.366 --> 50:06.894
Go talk to her.

50:28.953 --> 50:30.204
Calm the hell down!

50:30.704 --> 50:32.391
You seem so eager on being homeless!

50:32.891 --> 50:35.447
Do you care how my fate's gonna be
after you left?

50:35.988 --> 50:37.728
This is not your fault.

50:38.270 --> 50:39.647
Absolutely not.

50:39.672 --> 50:40.839
However you gotta calm down.

50:40.881 --> 50:42.520
Calm the hell down.

50:42.545 --> 50:43.802
She's your mom.

50:43.842 --> 50:45.302
You just shut up when she's raging,

50:45.344 --> 50:47.680
- she'll calm down eventually.
- Here goes your pottery!

50:48.055 --> 50:49.846
Here goes your dream!

50:49.874 --> 50:51.640
And your career!

50:51.665 --> 50:53.041
Here's to being "mature".

50:53.118 --> 50:55.079
You think you're an adult?

50:55.104 --> 50:56.916
You think you can do anything?

50:57.823 --> 51:00.362
I don't wanna suffer like you
in this house.

51:01.009 --> 51:03.196
I'll destroy them all.

51:15.689 --> 51:16.732
You're crying?

51:17.363 --> 51:18.741
Did she yell at you again?

51:18.938 --> 51:21.755
Why does she keep doing that?

51:22.381 --> 51:23.632
What is it today?

51:23.657 --> 51:25.091
Good bye Mr. Liem.

51:25.816 --> 51:27.026
Nhi! Nhi!

51:37.075 --> 51:38.117
Nhi!

51:40.482 --> 51:41.525
Wait up!

51:47.757 --> 51:48.758
Stop!

51:58.542 --> 52:00.335
Chasing you almost kills me.

52:05.090 --> 52:06.133
Take it.

52:09.344 --> 52:11.024
What is it?

52:11.067 --> 52:13.458
You can't run away with no money.

52:15.068 --> 52:16.778
I did it, so I know.

52:18.481 --> 52:19.772
Life is cruel.

52:20.439 --> 52:21.482
Here's the money.

52:22.566 --> 52:23.609
Take it.

52:27.946 --> 52:29.397
Come back when you're out.

52:30.745 --> 52:32.199
Don't just leave.

52:34.328 --> 52:35.412
Here you go.

52:40.209 --> 52:41.330
Grandma!

52:43.527 --> 52:45.137
Watch your health!

52:45.522 --> 52:46.523
I know.

52:46.548 --> 52:47.883
Stop gambling!

52:47.908 --> 52:49.076
Fuck you.

52:51.647 --> 52:53.030
Why didn't you stop her?

52:53.055 --> 52:56.366
This day is bound to come
between the two of them.

52:56.824 --> 52:59.005
Let them be, they're old enough.

52:59.030 --> 53:00.532
They've got to work it out.

53:35.170 --> 53:37.088
You're a vicious woman.

53:37.557 --> 53:38.933
I don't wanna live with you anymore.

53:39.104 --> 53:40.480
I want a divorce!

53:42.746 --> 53:45.249
Why are you treating us like this?

53:45.274 --> 53:46.650
Why are you leaving?

53:46.650 --> 53:48.902
What did I ever do?

53:53.824 --> 53:55.033
Stop crying.

53:56.087 --> 53:57.380
Get used to it.

54:30.194 --> 54:31.403
[I ran away.]

54:39.682 --> 54:42.434
[I'm at the bus stop near the school.
Can you pick me up?]

54:55.802 --> 54:57.763
[Wait for me]

55:10.150 --> 55:12.678
Leaving the house means you're
going against me.

56:19.096 --> 56:22.975
The number you dialed is not in service.
Please call...

56:28.562 --> 56:30.147
The number you dialed...

56:34.234 --> 56:36.528
...please call again later.

57:06.722 --> 57:07.807
Nhi!

57:22.699 --> 57:23.784
I'm sorry.

57:46.056 --> 57:47.332
Pay for the ride.

57:47.547 --> 57:49.130
- What?
- Pay for your ride.

58:00.799 --> 58:01.967
Who's that?

58:03.490 --> 58:05.033
What are the two of you doing here?

58:05.058 --> 58:06.813
- We ran away!
- What?

58:09.704 --> 58:11.890
- Only 500 bucks per month.
- This is okay.

58:11.915 --> 58:12.958
Isn't it reasonable?

58:12.999 --> 58:14.379
But that's not all.

58:18.880 --> 58:20.006
This is beautiful!

58:20.382 --> 58:21.591
Make way!

58:23.128 --> 58:25.130
Wait! This is yours! And yours!

58:28.890 --> 58:31.392
I worked so hard to find this place.

58:42.362 --> 58:43.536
Clean the house!

58:43.834 --> 58:46.003
With everything that we have prepared,

58:47.200 --> 58:48.493
we were ready

58:48.518 --> 58:51.011
to start an independent life.

58:54.496 --> 58:56.126
The cafe will succeed.

58:56.168 --> 58:57.127
I trust you.

58:57.227 --> 58:58.562
You're John.

58:58.587 --> 59:00.839
Of course! Thank you for introducing Manh.

59:00.839 --> 59:03.467
Everyone, here's object of the day.

59:03.492 --> 59:05.718
- How long do we have?
- Three days.

59:06.281 --> 59:09.024
This is the first time I get to
do what I like.

59:10.444 --> 59:12.193
To choose the person I love.

59:15.353 --> 59:17.564
All I want for my life...

59:18.857 --> 59:20.233
was just that simple.

59:20.233 --> 59:21.902
John!

59:22.089 --> 59:24.185
I cooked you lunch.

59:25.322 --> 59:27.073
I know you were tired
so I wanted to treat you.

59:27.073 --> 59:29.284
- Thank you baby!
- You should eat!

59:29.927 --> 59:32.096
I just wish mom could understand...

59:45.091 --> 59:46.760
Why are you running away?

59:47.010 --> 59:48.220
Here's the sweet soup.

59:48.261 --> 59:50.190
Why do you keep giving me
green beans?

59:50.215 --> 59:52.574
I know you're sick of it,
so it's aloe my dear.

59:52.599 --> 59:54.142
Aloe has a smell.

59:54.184 --> 59:56.061
- I don't like it.
- I know.

59:56.102 --> 59:57.938
So I cooked it with green beans.

59:59.773 --> 01:00:00.982
Enjoy!

01:00:03.568 --> 01:00:04.694
Oh there's this one thing.

01:00:04.736 --> 01:00:06.238
I've been wanting to tell you.

01:00:06.279 --> 01:00:07.489
About Nhi.

01:00:07.656 --> 01:00:09.658
Don't think I'm too nosy.

01:00:10.951 --> 01:00:13.703
Just let her fall in love normally,

01:00:13.703 --> 01:00:16.248
then she'll break up normally.

01:00:16.456 --> 01:00:19.251
She got it so far just because
you got it so hard.

01:00:20.335 --> 01:00:23.063
You're bound to fall in love
when you're young.

01:00:23.088 --> 01:00:25.172
It's not like you're gonna marry
your first love!

01:00:27.050 --> 01:00:28.969
No one can be faithful forever.

01:00:29.928 --> 01:00:31.304
Except me.

01:00:33.348 --> 01:00:35.376
Okay, forget it.

01:00:45.502 --> 01:00:47.504
[September]

01:00:47.529 --> 01:00:49.531
Sir, your card balance is not
enough to pay.

01:00:49.840 --> 01:00:51.091
Please check it over.

01:00:51.116 --> 01:00:52.367
I did check a few times.

01:00:59.249 --> 01:01:00.684
You're leaving your parents

01:01:00.709 --> 01:01:02.894
for a crab noodle girl,

01:01:02.919 --> 01:01:04.504
do you think it's worth it?

01:01:11.970 --> 01:01:13.680
Here comes food!

01:01:13.722 --> 01:01:15.432
We were just talking about you.

01:01:15.765 --> 01:01:16.891
- Prepare the food please.
- Okay.

01:01:16.933 --> 01:01:19.267
You guys start first, I'll go
wash my face.

01:01:19.511 --> 01:01:21.837
Babe, why is it this beef
and not the wagyu?

01:01:22.939 --> 01:01:24.159
Maybe I picked up the wrong one.

01:01:24.184 --> 01:01:25.719
Why is there only one clam tray?

01:01:26.112 --> 01:01:28.197
- I bought a few.
- No, there's only one.

01:01:28.222 --> 01:01:29.347
Look.

01:01:29.854 --> 01:01:31.072
Must have fallen out then.

01:01:31.181 --> 01:01:32.224
Fallen out?

01:01:32.453 --> 01:01:35.074
- I'll go get more then.
- No need.

01:01:35.410 --> 01:01:37.078
You took more than an hour,

01:01:37.103 --> 01:01:38.980
to buy these things?

01:01:39.205 --> 01:01:40.624
You've been strange recently.

01:01:40.665 --> 01:01:42.284
Your whereabouts are mysterious.

01:01:43.001 --> 01:01:44.210
Tell me the truth.

01:01:44.784 --> 01:01:45.879
Where have you been?

01:01:45.904 --> 01:01:47.175
Why do you ask me like that?

01:01:47.200 --> 01:01:49.452
I only went to get food
and you get jealous? Seriously?

01:01:49.585 --> 01:01:50.972
Why are you grumpy?

01:01:51.426 --> 01:01:53.371
Did I say anything wrong?

01:01:53.396 --> 01:01:55.368
I only asked you for two things.

01:01:55.722 --> 01:01:57.324
You got the wrong beef,

01:01:57.349 --> 01:01:59.001
then "dropped" the clam tray.

01:01:59.017 --> 01:02:00.493
Are the clam trays that light?

01:02:00.518 --> 01:02:01.686
They can be dropped without you knowing?

01:02:01.728 --> 01:02:03.874
Now you ask me to believe
that silly excuse?

01:02:05.396 --> 01:02:06.480
Come on.

01:02:06.505 --> 01:02:07.877
- Isn't that right?
- Let it go.

01:02:07.971 --> 01:02:10.919
How can you ask me not to
doubt you when your story is so nonsense?

01:02:13.031 --> 01:02:14.282
I'm definitely broke.

01:02:14.949 --> 01:02:16.576
I couldn't afford wagyu beef,

01:02:16.701 --> 01:02:18.870
so I lied that I got the wrong one, okay?

01:02:19.587 --> 01:02:22.131
One hangs out with friends at home,
waits for food.

01:02:22.156 --> 01:02:24.005
While one runs out of money
without understanding from the other.

01:02:24.209 --> 01:02:26.184
Have you ever thought about
how much I have left?

01:02:26.659 --> 01:02:27.642
John!

01:02:28.173 --> 01:02:30.216
Money is a sensitive subject!

01:02:30.493 --> 01:02:32.745
How could I know how much
you have left?

01:02:33.125 --> 01:02:35.316
Just tell me rather than
being that stupidly angry.

01:02:38.056 --> 01:02:39.140
I'm not angry.

01:02:40.183 --> 01:02:41.284
I'm frustrated!

01:02:43.832 --> 01:02:45.457
This is our life.

01:02:45.550 --> 01:02:47.123
But all you've ever done

01:02:47.148 --> 01:02:49.134
was enjoying it.

01:02:49.159 --> 01:02:50.568
And all I have to do

01:02:50.610 --> 01:02:52.823
is to face all the difficulties
out there.

01:02:52.848 --> 01:02:54.906
You better pick up a job
instead of a fight.

01:02:54.931 --> 01:02:56.041
John.

01:03:00.307 --> 01:03:01.670
Carry the baby!

01:03:02.789 --> 01:03:04.249
Then I'll go get a job.

01:03:12.257 --> 01:03:14.901
Why are you taking this out on me,

01:03:14.926 --> 01:03:17.462
while you were the one who said
I should stay home and rest,

01:03:17.487 --> 01:03:18.863
don't do anything.

01:03:18.888 --> 01:03:20.724
Now you're saying the opposite?

01:03:21.141 --> 01:03:22.892
You got a great excuse.

01:03:23.460 --> 01:03:25.689
Always the baby.

01:03:26.182 --> 01:03:27.589
There's no point in arguing with you.

01:03:28.327 --> 01:03:29.328
Okay.

01:03:30.358 --> 01:03:31.401
You win.

01:03:32.444 --> 01:03:33.964
John! John!

01:03:34.337 --> 01:03:35.724
- John!
- Dat!

01:03:35.752 --> 01:03:36.795
Let him be.

01:03:36.948 --> 01:03:38.491
He's been quiet combative recently.

01:03:38.533 --> 01:03:39.777
Let's eat.

01:03:39.802 --> 01:03:42.258
Nhi, why are you so aggressive?

01:03:42.475 --> 01:03:45.144
He's probably in a bad mood
because he ran out of money.

01:03:45.169 --> 01:03:46.566
This is not the first time.

01:03:50.203 --> 01:03:51.795
Just like any other couple,

01:03:52.024 --> 01:03:56.706
our love starts to face stupid
problems of the youth.

01:03:57.527 --> 01:04:00.113
Each person only cares about
what they're doing,

01:04:00.138 --> 01:04:02.190
rather than the feelings
of the other person.

01:04:02.215 --> 01:04:04.009
How's hugging Mr. Manh's sister?

01:04:04.128 --> 01:04:06.578
This is for business.
You shouldn't be jealous babe.

01:04:06.603 --> 01:04:08.938
No you looked happy here.

01:04:08.938 --> 01:04:11.488
And when the problems have
built up long enough,

01:04:11.941 --> 01:04:14.108
people won't even bother explaining things.

01:04:14.266 --> 01:04:16.060
What's that attitude?

01:04:16.096 --> 01:04:18.631
You're leaving now?
You're leaving now?

01:04:18.656 --> 01:04:20.492
Nhuan! Can't you hear me?

01:04:20.533 --> 01:04:21.826
At Nhu's age,

01:04:21.826 --> 01:04:24.019
she can't even figure out her problems.

01:04:24.876 --> 01:04:26.461
Let alone us,

01:04:27.582 --> 01:04:30.084
the twenty-something young adults.

01:04:30.335 --> 01:04:31.669
Combative,

01:04:31.904 --> 01:04:33.322
insensitive,

01:04:33.845 --> 01:04:37.071
then upset each other
over stupid things.

01:04:55.318 --> 01:04:58.112
Don't ever talk to me
if you call him.

01:05:05.870 --> 01:05:07.539
Where did you get this money?

01:05:07.539 --> 01:05:08.790
I saved up.

01:05:08.832 --> 01:05:10.792
Where did you get money to save?
Did you steal from me?

01:05:10.834 --> 01:05:13.378
Nhu, watch your mouth.

01:05:13.586 --> 01:05:14.629
Sometimes,

01:05:14.879 --> 01:05:16.529
during the heat,

01:05:16.965 --> 01:05:19.532
we become overbearing
like a habit.

01:05:20.385 --> 01:05:21.719
So much so that...

01:05:22.053 --> 01:05:24.472
we ourselves can't even realize it.

01:05:24.603 --> 01:05:26.609
- Can't you hear me?
- Let go of me.

01:05:27.100 --> 01:05:28.560
Have some boundaries.

01:05:28.601 --> 01:05:30.232
Listen to me, Nhuan!

01:05:37.151 --> 01:05:38.736
In a relationship,

01:05:38.820 --> 01:05:41.114
it's hard when

01:05:41.518 --> 01:05:42.769
no one's right,

01:05:43.324 --> 01:05:44.750
and no one's wrong.

01:05:45.493 --> 01:05:47.495
We only have different perspectives.

01:05:48.204 --> 01:05:49.414
And then

01:05:49.473 --> 01:05:51.141
there's no sympathy.

01:05:52.041 --> 01:05:53.626
Then we slowly grow apart.

01:06:10.493 --> 01:06:11.911
You can't leave me now.

01:06:11.936 --> 01:06:13.738
I've put all the money in,

01:06:13.763 --> 01:06:15.014
construction already started,

01:06:15.039 --> 01:06:16.624
saying that now is like killing me.

01:06:16.649 --> 01:06:17.734
Listen to...

01:06:17.861 --> 01:06:18.903
Hey!

01:06:21.310 --> 01:06:22.394
Damn it.

01:06:22.419 --> 01:06:23.406
Fuck!

01:06:33.622 --> 01:06:37.795
[October]

01:06:38.746 --> 01:06:41.265
A sad afternoon at the
Thu Duc crab noodle restaurant.

01:06:41.290 --> 01:06:42.792
It's Le Minh Ho again.

01:06:42.817 --> 01:06:44.527
Look, it's quite empty here.

01:06:44.552 --> 01:06:47.347
Let's get closer to see
what happened.

01:06:47.372 --> 01:06:48.706
Let's go.

01:06:50.058 --> 01:06:51.768
I almost got run over,
but that's okay,

01:06:51.793 --> 01:06:53.077
here here, have a look.

01:06:53.102 --> 01:06:54.270
See?

01:06:54.295 --> 01:06:56.039
Not a whole lot of people,

01:06:56.064 --> 01:06:57.148
the crab pile is big,

01:06:57.173 --> 01:06:58.666
and the pork is even bigger.

01:06:58.691 --> 01:07:01.152
From now on, the boss
will no longer yell at the customers.

01:07:01.204 --> 01:07:02.128
Why?

01:07:02.153 --> 01:07:03.613
- There's no customer to yell at.
- Son of a bitch!

01:07:03.613 --> 01:07:05.724
- Go away!
- She just swore at my mom.

01:07:06.141 --> 01:07:08.718
There's no reason for you
to record here.

01:07:08.743 --> 01:07:10.536
It's you who scared my customers away.

01:07:10.687 --> 01:07:13.357
- Go away!
- Has she called recently?

01:07:18.586 --> 01:07:20.296
- Hello.
- Hello Nhu.

01:07:20.321 --> 01:07:21.864
Forgot how to use a phone?

01:07:21.944 --> 01:07:23.938
How's grandma and mom?

01:07:24.242 --> 01:07:25.369
Grandma's fine.

01:07:25.588 --> 01:07:26.631
Mom's sick,

01:07:26.656 --> 01:07:28.116
you should visit her.

01:07:28.491 --> 01:07:29.534
Is that so?

01:07:29.864 --> 01:07:30.740
But...

01:07:30.765 --> 01:07:32.433
Can you lend me a thousand bucks?

01:07:32.475 --> 01:07:34.852
What have you been doing
that now you have to borrow from me?

01:07:36.007 --> 01:07:37.342
Answer me.

01:07:38.734 --> 01:07:40.006
How's your baby?

01:07:40.201 --> 01:07:41.996
I'm six months along.

01:07:42.021 --> 01:07:43.586
Where's the baby father?

01:07:43.611 --> 01:07:45.029
Let's talk about it later.

01:07:45.054 --> 01:07:46.389
Just lend me some.

01:07:46.414 --> 01:07:47.657
My sales has been so slow.

01:07:47.699 --> 01:07:50.013
I'll try to send half by
the end of the month.

01:07:50.188 --> 01:07:51.230
Listen,

01:07:51.264 --> 01:07:53.631
it wouldn't kill you to
come home and apologize.

01:07:53.656 --> 01:07:55.573
You two are exactly the same.

01:07:55.598 --> 01:07:58.059
Just send me the money when you can.
Thank you.

01:07:58.084 --> 01:07:59.168
Hey! Hey!

01:08:00.003 --> 01:08:01.879
- This kid!
- What did she say?

01:08:01.921 --> 01:08:04.660
Ran away with that dude
and now she's borrowing money.

01:08:05.717 --> 01:08:06.926
What now?

01:08:07.719 --> 01:08:10.096
Oh Anh? Sorry, I thought you were
my sister.

01:08:12.791 --> 01:08:13.698
What?

01:08:14.103 --> 01:08:15.187
My husband what?

01:08:30.908 --> 01:08:31.951
Nhuan!

01:08:32.563 --> 01:08:34.023
You look happy, don't you?

01:08:37.181 --> 01:08:38.558
Who are you? Let go!

01:08:38.583 --> 01:08:39.917
Nhu, stop.

01:08:39.917 --> 01:08:41.085
Let me go!

01:08:41.127 --> 01:08:42.792
You're picking her side?

01:08:43.838 --> 01:08:45.423
Come on, come on!

01:08:45.903 --> 01:08:47.208
Calm down ladies!

01:08:51.262 --> 01:08:53.042
Let her go!

01:08:57.375 --> 01:08:59.554
- Dinner yet?
- Already!

01:09:07.904 --> 01:09:09.175
Hey Quynh.

01:09:09.781 --> 01:09:11.750
The dudes that partnered with me

01:09:12.116 --> 01:09:13.485
just dropped out.

01:09:13.540 --> 01:09:14.844
Can you lend me 50 thousand bucks?

01:09:14.869 --> 01:09:16.037
You're talking about 50 grands man.

01:09:16.079 --> 01:09:17.984
I've told you from the beginning,
they don't look reliable,

01:09:18.009 --> 01:09:20.755
- and you still trusted them.
- I know.

01:09:24.103 --> 01:09:26.606
Can you grab me a band-aid John?

01:09:26.631 --> 01:09:29.192
It's in the drawer by the fish,
can you grab it yourself?

01:09:29.217 --> 01:09:32.053
- I'm on the phone.
- I'm in pain, get it for me please.

01:09:32.078 --> 01:09:33.267
I'll call you back.

01:09:39.143 --> 01:09:41.579
It's here, it's right here.

01:09:41.604 --> 01:09:43.022
I said I was on the phone.

01:09:43.047 --> 01:09:44.965
Can't you see I'm bleeding?

01:09:45.274 --> 01:09:47.193
I'm carrying a baby too,
how can I go get it?

01:09:47.218 --> 01:09:49.292
Is it that difficult to
get me a band-aid?

01:09:50.170 --> 01:09:51.338
Fine, I'm sorry.

01:09:53.821 --> 01:09:56.260
I've never seen such a
petty man.

01:09:56.285 --> 01:09:58.990
I didn't think you're still angry about
that hot pot thing.

01:10:00.248 --> 01:10:02.416
Bickering over a tiny band-aid.

01:10:03.808 --> 01:10:04.804
Hey!

01:10:05.318 --> 01:10:06.813
We've cleared that.

01:10:06.838 --> 01:10:08.047
I'm not mad at you.

01:10:08.101 --> 01:10:09.481
I'm not that petty.

01:10:09.641 --> 01:10:12.426
I didn't grab it for you
because I was on the phone.

01:10:12.451 --> 01:10:14.078
I was working on my thing.

01:10:14.679 --> 01:10:17.339
Why are you picking a fight
over a band-aid?

01:10:17.460 --> 01:10:18.544
What's wrong with you?

01:10:18.788 --> 01:10:20.164
Don't you think that's too much?

01:10:22.353 --> 01:10:24.375
John, you've changed.

01:10:25.231 --> 01:10:28.407
Once people fell out of love,
nothing is important anymore.

01:10:29.045 --> 01:10:32.132
How can I be as important
as your phone call with a friend?

01:10:32.157 --> 01:10:33.325
Let me see.

01:10:39.881 --> 01:10:40.770
Nhi!

01:10:42.456 --> 01:10:44.665
Me changing is not the problem,

01:10:45.006 --> 01:10:47.677
the problem is you're
refusing to change.

01:10:48.734 --> 01:10:51.040
What do you do? Nothing.

01:10:51.065 --> 01:10:54.110
I'm working everyday to make money,
what more do you want?

01:10:54.135 --> 01:10:56.053
I put over 50 thousands bucks
in that cafe,

01:10:56.095 --> 01:10:57.346
and my partners just dropped.

01:10:57.346 --> 01:10:59.490
Where am I getting the money
to finish that now?

01:10:59.515 --> 01:11:00.641
You don't care about those things,

01:11:00.666 --> 01:11:03.161
you only want to pick fights
over a band-aid,

01:11:03.186 --> 01:11:04.270
what's wrong with you?

01:11:07.773 --> 01:11:09.567
The problem is not the band-aid.

01:11:11.180 --> 01:11:13.808
It's your attitude towards me.

01:11:14.255 --> 01:11:17.425
You've made all the decisions,
I quit my job because you asked me to.

01:11:17.450 --> 01:11:18.743
You said you'll take care of me.

01:11:18.768 --> 01:11:20.511
Because you're John.

01:11:20.536 --> 01:11:23.899
And now you're talking like I'm
an ungrateful parasite.

01:11:24.070 --> 01:11:26.316
You wanted to take care of everything.

01:11:26.341 --> 01:11:29.094
Now that you can't handle it,
you said I don't care about you?

01:11:29.266 --> 01:11:31.631
How could I know if you keep
keeping your mouth shut?

01:11:31.656 --> 01:11:33.577
If you wanted to know, you'd know.

01:11:34.432 --> 01:11:36.266
You'll find out anything you wanna know.

01:11:36.731 --> 01:11:39.614
You even know how many photos
there are on a tiny phone.

01:11:39.639 --> 01:11:41.140
Okay, I'm insane.

01:11:46.312 --> 01:11:47.980
Only an insane person would
leave her home,

01:11:47.980 --> 01:11:49.273
her family,

01:11:49.298 --> 01:11:51.508
to give you all the money she has.

01:11:52.026 --> 01:11:53.236
How much did you give?

01:11:53.261 --> 01:11:55.448
Almost 1500 bucks.

01:11:55.664 --> 01:11:58.098
And you're comparing that to
50 thousand dollars?

01:11:58.123 --> 01:11:59.562
Doesn't that sound ridiculous to you?

01:12:04.205 --> 01:12:08.141
It's ridiculous because to you,
it's just 1500 bucks.

01:12:09.352 --> 01:12:12.647
But if you consider it's every single cent
I've saved,

01:12:12.672 --> 01:12:16.309
even all my grandma
gave me when I ran away with you,

01:12:16.915 --> 01:12:18.917
you wouldn't be laughing.

01:12:33.088 --> 01:12:35.507
I'm always the fight-picker
in your eyes.

01:12:37.217 --> 01:12:40.428
But those are just silly things
any girl would do,

01:12:42.706 --> 01:12:45.500
to seek some attention
from her man.

01:12:46.130 --> 01:12:48.465
I can see you're stressed from work.

01:12:49.048 --> 01:12:51.057
But I'm pregnant.

01:12:54.430 --> 01:12:55.962
I'm stressed too.

01:12:56.463 --> 01:13:00.040
My hormones changed,
I'm easily depressed.

01:13:03.050 --> 01:13:05.192
And that's what you can't see.

01:13:12.106 --> 01:13:14.239
Bastard! Answer me.

01:13:14.609 --> 01:13:16.360
How can you treat me like that?

01:13:16.563 --> 01:13:18.440
How long have you been with her?

01:13:20.239 --> 01:13:21.318
Say it!

01:13:22.510 --> 01:13:25.096
- I don't...
- You don't need to say a thing.

01:13:25.121 --> 01:13:27.874
You had an affair and
now what're you gonna say?

01:13:27.899 --> 01:13:29.890
I caught you red-handed and
you're denying it?

01:13:29.915 --> 01:13:31.917
- I'm not denying.
- Then you don't need to say anything.

01:13:31.917 --> 01:13:34.735
I know exactly what you wanna say
anytime you open your mouth.

01:13:34.760 --> 01:13:36.303
Grandma, do you know who she was?

01:13:36.328 --> 01:13:38.333
She's my customer.

01:13:38.358 --> 01:13:41.501
The little slutty Chubby Piggy.
That bitch!

01:13:41.804 --> 01:13:45.156
I've had my suspicion. She'd always take
your side when I yell at you on stream.

01:13:45.181 --> 01:13:48.142
I've been treating her like a VIP.

01:13:48.184 --> 01:13:50.219
Sending my own husband to
deliver her orders.

01:13:50.244 --> 01:13:52.955
She got the packages and
got my husband too, isn't that neat?

01:13:52.980 --> 01:13:54.398
Just perfect!

01:13:55.710 --> 01:13:56.794
What now?

01:13:56.940 --> 01:13:58.692
How are you gonna solve this?

01:14:00.026 --> 01:14:02.529
You're dead to me
if you mess it up.

01:14:04.950 --> 01:14:07.572
That was bad Nhuan.

01:14:07.597 --> 01:14:09.391
Why did you cheat?

01:14:19.215 --> 01:14:21.250
Can you let me divorce her?

01:14:21.801 --> 01:14:23.027
I'm tired.

01:14:23.052 --> 01:14:24.053
Oh my gosh!

01:14:24.078 --> 01:14:25.847
What the hell did you just say?

01:14:26.029 --> 01:14:27.406
You have to apologize.

01:14:27.431 --> 01:14:29.288
Are you insane? What did you say?

01:14:29.313 --> 01:14:30.993
You have to apologize.
You out of your mind?

01:14:31.018 --> 01:14:32.725
Stop it!

01:14:34.164 --> 01:14:36.458
How can he talk if
you won't shut up?

01:14:37.796 --> 01:14:39.188
How aggressive you are!

01:14:39.563 --> 01:14:41.231
Who did you learn that from?

01:14:41.398 --> 01:14:42.649
It's all your fault.

01:14:43.364 --> 01:14:46.909
You told me he loved you
with all that he had.

01:14:46.992 --> 01:14:48.520
You picked him.

01:14:48.545 --> 01:14:50.671
Now you have to take responsibility.

01:14:51.325 --> 01:14:52.493
And you.

01:14:53.324 --> 01:14:55.493
What's your relationship with her?

01:14:55.918 --> 01:14:57.954
I wanna hear it from you.

01:15:04.844 --> 01:15:07.304
We just started recently.

01:15:09.473 --> 01:15:10.558
But...

01:15:12.977 --> 01:15:14.061
Well...

01:15:19.908 --> 01:15:21.082
Whatever.

01:15:21.610 --> 01:15:23.910
Just let me stop this.

01:15:23.938 --> 01:15:25.523
I don't want to live like this anymore.

01:15:27.783 --> 01:15:29.368
What does she have that I don't?

01:15:29.796 --> 01:15:33.174
What does she have that make you
treat me like this?

01:15:35.332 --> 01:15:37.553
It's not because of what she has.

01:15:39.571 --> 01:15:42.189
It's that I feel like a man
being with her.

01:15:42.214 --> 01:15:45.102
What did I ever do that make you
don't feel like a man?

01:15:45.127 --> 01:15:46.629
What did I do,

01:15:46.654 --> 01:15:49.806
- tell me what I did.
- You're doing it now.

01:15:53.184 --> 01:15:56.103
I don't really have a chance to
finish my sentences in this family.

01:15:57.938 --> 01:16:00.357
You'd cut in to scream at me,
or she would.

01:16:03.277 --> 01:16:06.280
There's nothing I can do
to please your family.

01:16:06.322 --> 01:16:07.323
Excuse me.

01:16:07.323 --> 01:16:09.825
I'm only helping out in the house
because I love the family.

01:16:09.867 --> 01:16:12.815
I could've gotten a better job
anywhere else.

01:16:13.146 --> 01:16:15.208
They'd pay me, maybe even more
than you are.

01:16:15.671 --> 01:16:17.381
They'd respect me too.

01:16:17.406 --> 01:16:18.991
Give me a reason to respect you.

01:16:19.016 --> 01:16:21.059
What have you done to earn that respect?

01:16:21.812 --> 01:16:23.522
You deliver your wife's packages,

01:16:23.547 --> 01:16:26.220
then help at the restaurant,
then you get paid.

01:16:26.317 --> 01:16:27.318
Then you go drinking!

01:16:27.343 --> 01:16:30.669
Your life is so easy, can't you see that?

01:16:30.694 --> 01:16:32.239
What do you want?

01:16:32.264 --> 01:16:34.141
If you want to be respected,
you have to strive.

01:16:34.166 --> 01:16:35.581
I do strive.

01:16:41.607 --> 01:16:43.538
I do! I really do!

01:16:43.563 --> 01:16:45.403
I do everyday.

01:16:45.428 --> 01:16:46.785
Only you couldn't see.

01:16:47.540 --> 01:16:51.165
You only look at people's weaknesses,
never the strength.

01:16:52.701 --> 01:16:54.954
How can you say I'm not striving?

01:16:58.666 --> 01:17:00.501
I have my bad traits, of course.

01:17:00.543 --> 01:17:02.311
My stinky farts, my smelly body.

01:17:02.336 --> 01:17:04.755
I made less money than you,

01:17:04.780 --> 01:17:06.815
but at least I'm not stealing
from anyone.

01:17:06.840 --> 01:17:08.175
And when I'm out to drink,

01:17:08.200 --> 01:17:11.537
I just like being around friends,
to have a chat.

01:17:11.562 --> 01:17:13.489
Because sometimes I get drunk,

01:17:13.514 --> 01:17:16.626
and while I'm drunk,
I don't feel belittled.

01:17:16.651 --> 01:17:21.310
You keep screaming at me
for no apparent reason.

01:17:21.335 --> 01:17:24.553
No striving would ever be enough
for the two of you.

01:17:25.401 --> 01:17:27.278
If I'm that bad of a man,

01:17:27.319 --> 01:17:29.079
why don't you just find someone else?

01:17:29.104 --> 01:17:30.865
And if they're that good of a man,

01:17:30.890 --> 01:17:32.759
will they tolerate you?

01:17:32.844 --> 01:17:34.053
Nhuan!

01:17:34.313 --> 01:17:36.416
You're the cheater, you're in the wrong.

01:17:36.441 --> 01:17:39.569
Why are you making it sound like
we're the ones at fault?

01:17:40.207 --> 01:17:42.548
It's my fault, I know that.

01:17:42.960 --> 01:17:45.915
I've been wanting to stop so many times.

01:17:46.848 --> 01:17:48.816
I know I was wrong.
I told myself...

01:17:48.841 --> 01:17:51.068
I'll call it quit with her,

01:17:51.093 --> 01:17:52.914
and come home to my wife,
however...

01:17:53.147 --> 01:17:54.774
everytime I come home...

01:17:54.822 --> 01:17:56.532
you two just push me further.

01:17:56.557 --> 01:17:57.808
I've really...

01:17:59.156 --> 01:18:01.192
tried my best

01:18:01.525 --> 01:18:04.050
not to let this happen.

01:18:04.601 --> 01:18:06.333
I've tried.

01:18:07.902 --> 01:18:09.708
Everyone is guilty...

01:18:10.985 --> 01:18:12.432
Every single one.

01:18:13.037 --> 01:18:16.108
But why do everyone think
they're the victims?

01:18:16.827 --> 01:18:18.206
Nhuan, where are you going?

01:18:18.231 --> 01:18:19.910
Nhuan! Nhuan!

01:18:20.172 --> 01:18:24.198
I scream at you a lot but
I always take your side.

01:18:24.402 --> 01:18:29.570
Why did you let it go this far that
I can't even try to be on your side?

01:18:34.806 --> 01:18:35.974
Fine, I'm sorry.

01:18:36.180 --> 01:18:37.348
You don't need to.

01:18:39.693 --> 01:18:40.944
I have to take responsibility.

01:18:46.487 --> 01:18:50.081
I regret believing that a douchebag
like you can bring me happiness.

01:18:52.071 --> 01:18:53.197
Douchebag?

01:18:56.119 --> 01:18:57.910
Then let this douchebag tell you this.

01:18:59.481 --> 01:19:02.651
I kinda regret picking this life for you.

01:19:05.310 --> 01:19:08.296
If you were more careful,
we would've been much better.

01:19:08.321 --> 01:19:09.948
If we didn't have the baby,

01:19:09.980 --> 01:19:11.357
and your mom didn't mess
everything up,

01:19:11.382 --> 01:19:13.300
my life would have been much happier,

01:19:13.300 --> 01:19:15.511
instead of working my ass off

01:19:15.536 --> 01:19:17.173
and standing here arguing with you.

01:19:17.761 --> 01:19:19.733
You chose the baby.

01:19:19.939 --> 01:19:22.788
I don't even know how to be a father.

01:19:22.813 --> 01:19:24.728
You mean I tricked you?

01:19:24.753 --> 01:19:27.695
I mean you have total control
over this matter.

01:19:27.720 --> 01:19:30.292
- If you didn't want...
- It's because I trusted you.

01:19:30.317 --> 01:19:31.522
Son of a bitch!

01:19:37.637 --> 01:19:39.209
I don't need your picking my side.

01:19:39.811 --> 01:19:41.465
I need your respect.

01:19:43.956 --> 01:19:46.208
I've saved up five ounces of gold.

01:19:47.334 --> 01:19:49.010
I'll leave them for you and Nhu.

01:19:55.259 --> 01:19:56.564
I'm sorry grandma.

01:19:57.720 --> 01:19:59.002
It's all my fault.

01:20:00.723 --> 01:20:02.013
I'm sorry mom.

01:20:03.100 --> 01:20:04.345
- Sorry Nhu.
- Nhuan!

01:20:04.599 --> 01:20:06.684
Do you have to take it this far?

01:20:08.357 --> 01:20:10.190
That's the question I want
to ask you everyday.

01:20:10.215 --> 01:20:11.666
You're being disrespectful.

01:20:12.327 --> 01:20:14.753
Can you talk without smashing things?

01:20:14.778 --> 01:20:16.697
Can you watch your mouth?

01:20:16.722 --> 01:20:18.265
You're becoming your mother.

01:20:18.290 --> 01:20:19.477
Shut the fuck up John!

01:20:20.674 --> 01:20:22.241
I won't live with you anymore.

01:20:22.266 --> 01:20:23.842
- You're a terrible person.
- Stop!

01:20:24.720 --> 01:20:26.898
The more you speak,
the worse you get.

01:20:27.079 --> 01:20:29.539
- Apologize to me.
- Apologize my ass!

01:20:29.564 --> 01:20:31.044
Get the hell out of my life!

01:20:31.069 --> 01:20:33.555
- Nhuan! Please!
- You don't have to stop him.

01:20:33.939 --> 01:20:36.525
He's determined to leave,
why keep him?

01:20:36.550 --> 01:20:37.676
Nhuan!

01:20:39.206 --> 01:20:41.478
People fall in love to stay.

01:20:42.097 --> 01:20:43.724
No one falls in love to leave.

01:20:43.749 --> 01:20:45.417
There has to be a reason to leave.

01:20:47.798 --> 01:20:49.475
Think it over mom.

01:20:50.023 --> 01:20:51.483
Did you do anything to dad?

01:20:52.271 --> 01:20:53.637
Or did he just leave?

01:20:54.707 --> 01:20:55.922
Go away!

01:20:57.675 --> 01:20:59.438
Okay. Fine.

01:21:00.029 --> 01:21:02.785
Nhuan, please don't leave me,
I love you, Nhuan!

01:21:02.826 --> 01:21:05.829
Please I'm begging you!

01:21:05.854 --> 01:21:07.726
Nhuan!

01:21:24.890 --> 01:21:26.725
You're a vicious woman.

01:21:27.351 --> 01:21:28.811
I don't wanna live with you anymore.

01:21:28.852 --> 01:21:30.062
I want a divorce.

01:21:30.854 --> 01:21:32.533
You're a vicious woman.

01:21:33.357 --> 01:21:34.858
I don't wanna live with you anymore.

01:21:35.609 --> 01:21:36.693
I want a divorce.

01:21:37.994 --> 01:21:39.713
I don't wanna live with you anymore.

01:21:40.325 --> 01:21:41.650
I don't wanna live with you anymore.

01:21:45.141 --> 01:21:46.961
In my mom's memory,

01:21:46.986 --> 01:21:48.819
dad was the only one at fault.

01:21:49.362 --> 01:21:50.996
And I believe that

01:21:51.972 --> 01:21:54.119
that's all she could ever see.

01:22:03.762 --> 01:22:06.010
She wouldn't understand that...

01:22:06.039 --> 01:22:07.667
Sometimes...

01:22:07.870 --> 01:22:10.590
- All dad needed was some compromise.
- Get out of my house.

01:22:11.186 --> 01:22:12.771
It's kinda late now,
can we talk tomorrow?

01:22:12.813 --> 01:22:15.774
No need to talk. Go sleep with your
friends if you like them that much.

01:22:15.799 --> 01:22:17.467
You're over-reacting over nothing.

01:22:17.492 --> 01:22:19.869
- Nothing? Nothing?
- Stop! Stop!

01:22:21.905 --> 01:22:23.828
Mom wouldn't understand that...

01:22:24.491 --> 01:22:25.742
A man

01:22:25.962 --> 01:22:28.262
needs his wife's respect
in front of his peers.

01:22:28.287 --> 01:22:30.247
You've got to listen to me
if you feel an ounce of shame.

01:22:30.289 --> 01:22:31.957
Your time must be spent with
your family,

01:22:31.999 --> 01:22:34.368
not with these useless beings.

01:22:34.393 --> 01:22:36.691
Stand up! Let's go!

01:22:36.716 --> 01:22:38.957
All the arguments

01:22:39.339 --> 01:22:41.455
have the same starting points.

01:22:41.538 --> 01:22:43.010
The conflict.

01:22:43.635 --> 01:22:45.837
But a different destination,

01:22:45.862 --> 01:22:47.357
depending on when you stop.

01:22:48.473 --> 01:22:50.490
Mom doesn't know when to stop.

01:22:53.854 --> 01:22:55.093
Enough!

01:22:56.610 --> 01:22:59.273
Why do you keep nagging?
Just let finish my meal.

01:22:59.298 --> 01:23:01.509
I have to nag to drill it
into your head.

01:23:01.896 --> 01:23:04.023
You always listen to your friends,

01:23:04.048 --> 01:23:05.841
they're more than your family.

01:23:05.866 --> 01:23:08.327
Then you come home and get upset at
your wife and kids.

01:23:08.971 --> 01:23:12.057
Such a big ego for being so damn useless!

01:23:16.387 --> 01:23:18.556
If I'm that useless, why do you
stay with me?

01:23:20.264 --> 01:23:21.868
When we're angry,

01:23:21.893 --> 01:23:24.354
we can only see the problems
coming from the other person.

01:23:24.379 --> 01:23:25.922
What do you think you're doing?

01:23:28.673 --> 01:23:30.883
We can only see that
we're mistreated,

01:23:30.908 --> 01:23:32.284
You can only bully me!

01:23:32.309 --> 01:23:35.103
and forget all the basic kindness
the other person deserves.

01:23:35.128 --> 01:23:36.867
You're a vicious woman.

01:23:37.147 --> 01:23:38.523
I don't wanna live with you anymore.

01:23:38.552 --> 01:23:39.904
I want a divorce.

01:23:42.002 --> 01:23:43.462
Why are you leaving?

01:23:43.487 --> 01:23:45.197
Nhuan, don't leave.

01:23:45.222 --> 01:23:48.321
- Tell me the reason.
- I'm begging you, Nhuan.

01:24:17.229 --> 01:24:19.703
I've never liked
Financial And Banking University

01:24:19.728 --> 01:24:21.242
even for a day.

01:24:21.858 --> 01:24:23.443
I did it for you.

01:25:11.074 --> 01:25:12.493
Here's some sweet soup.

01:25:13.493 --> 01:25:15.387
From Mr. Liem?

01:25:15.412 --> 01:25:16.455
Yeah.

01:25:18.498 --> 01:25:19.666
Where's Nhu?

01:25:20.333 --> 01:25:21.418
She's sleeping.

01:25:26.506 --> 01:25:28.175
We had such a big family,

01:25:30.010 --> 01:25:32.012
now all scattered away.

01:25:40.103 --> 01:25:41.813
Do you think I was wrong?

01:25:46.401 --> 01:25:47.736
Tell me...

01:25:50.864 --> 01:25:53.938
When was the last time you
apologize to someone?

01:26:30.237 --> 01:26:31.822
Why didn't you stop me?

01:26:31.947 --> 01:26:33.532
You wouldn't listen to me.

01:26:34.699 --> 01:26:37.282
Stand up where you fell.

01:26:38.161 --> 01:26:40.580
Don't make people do what you want.

01:26:41.706 --> 01:26:44.793
Nothing is absolute.

01:26:45.710 --> 01:26:47.796
Just circumstantial.

01:27:02.597 --> 01:27:03.641
Baby!

01:27:06.020 --> 01:27:07.049
Nhi!

01:27:27.395 --> 01:27:28.385
Robbery!

01:27:56.907 --> 01:27:58.355
Help! Anyone here?

01:29:06.005 --> 01:29:08.808
Mom, mom!

01:29:08.833 --> 01:29:12.403
Mom, please don't. Stop, please!

01:29:12.428 --> 01:29:13.833
Why did you do that?

01:29:13.858 --> 01:29:15.732
- Why did you kill my grandchild?
- Mom, please!

01:29:15.777 --> 01:29:17.013
- Why?
- Mom!

01:29:17.038 --> 01:29:19.216
- Why do you treat my daughter like that?
- Mom, please!

01:29:19.300 --> 01:29:22.081
- My grandchild!
- Mom!

01:29:26.162 --> 01:29:29.457
Do you know the difference between
school and the school of life?

01:29:31.793 --> 01:29:32.877
At school,

01:29:32.877 --> 01:29:34.045
we learn,

01:29:34.045 --> 01:29:35.505
then we do the test.

01:29:35.530 --> 01:29:37.007
[Months later]

01:29:37.032 --> 01:29:38.534
In the school of life,

01:29:38.559 --> 01:29:40.487
you do the test first,

01:29:40.512 --> 01:29:42.097
then learn your own lessons.

01:29:46.474 --> 01:29:48.618
You can't change someone's personality

01:29:48.643 --> 01:29:51.898
just because you want to.

01:29:55.108 --> 01:29:56.679
But they will change

01:29:57.233 --> 01:29:58.994
after they experience

01:30:01.448 --> 01:30:02.657
trauma.

01:30:08.705 --> 01:30:10.790
It will help us realize lots of things.

01:30:16.588 --> 01:30:18.173
...these girly styles are so sweet.

01:30:18.590 --> 01:30:21.731
Ever since that day, they went
no contact.

01:30:23.564 --> 01:30:25.816
Maybe Nhuan is somewhere...

01:30:25.841 --> 01:30:27.009
Being happy.

01:30:28.433 --> 01:30:29.907
Or unhappy.

01:30:31.833 --> 01:30:33.861
Whether we're happy or not,

01:30:34.105 --> 01:30:35.914
things keep moving.

01:30:46.784 --> 01:30:49.354
- Mom, here you are.
- Thank you.

01:30:49.379 --> 01:30:50.391
- See ya.
- Ok.

01:30:50.416 --> 01:30:51.594
Bye bye, grandma.

01:30:52.821 --> 01:30:55.742
Today, your daughter gave you milk tea,
so sweet.

01:30:56.031 --> 01:30:57.330
Here you go.

01:30:59.829 --> 01:31:01.491
So sweet! I love it!

01:31:05.053 --> 01:31:08.098
- Do you want your hair like mine?
- I'm old, girls.

01:31:08.123 --> 01:31:10.542
- Have the highlights then.
- Are you nuts?

01:31:10.567 --> 01:31:12.152
They'll think I'm a crazy lady, girls.

01:31:12.177 --> 01:31:14.221
Woman up! Try it!

01:31:15.105 --> 01:31:16.981
No, thanks.

01:31:17.006 --> 01:31:18.883
Gotta change up your style!

01:31:23.530 --> 01:31:25.031
- Hey!
- Yes?

01:31:26.574 --> 01:31:29.119
If I didn't forbid you and John,

01:31:29.160 --> 01:31:31.121
would you have a baby with him?

01:31:36.167 --> 01:31:38.128
Let bygones be bygones.

01:31:40.380 --> 01:31:41.965
Maybe she's not saying it,

01:31:42.204 --> 01:31:44.707
or maybe she will never say it.

01:31:44.968 --> 01:31:46.094
But I know

01:31:46.459 --> 01:31:48.857
she has something
she deeply wants to tell me.

01:31:52.946 --> 01:31:55.032
I named the baby Ngoc Nhien.

01:31:55.548 --> 01:31:57.634
Nhien means peaceful.

01:31:59.065 --> 01:32:01.359
I hope it will be in a better place.

01:32:02.110 --> 01:32:04.446
- Stop stop stop!
- Listen to me. All through the night!

01:32:04.533 --> 01:32:06.431
And when you choose to be optimistic...

01:32:06.473 --> 01:32:09.100
Excuse me, can I buy you a drink?

01:32:10.034 --> 01:32:11.327
New things

01:32:11.327 --> 01:32:12.579
will come to you.

01:32:15.874 --> 01:32:17.417
Believe me, he's not straight.

01:32:17.442 --> 01:32:20.812
- How about this one?
- Probably not either. He's got earrings!

01:32:22.755 --> 01:32:24.257
She will talk me out of it anyway.

01:32:24.299 --> 01:32:25.800
She won't change.

01:32:26.676 --> 01:32:28.094
What changed here

01:32:29.543 --> 01:32:31.712
is how she welcomes everything.

01:32:42.978 --> 01:32:44.319
Some people

01:32:44.360 --> 01:32:46.613
will try to stay by your side.

01:32:46.766 --> 01:32:48.643
Not knowing what they
will get in return.

01:32:48.936 --> 01:32:50.979
New bowls new bowls!
Where do you want them boss?

01:32:51.004 --> 01:32:52.965
- Let Lan check them please.
- Okay.

01:32:54.621 --> 01:32:56.927
Be careful! They're ceramics,
not metals.

01:32:56.952 --> 01:32:58.162
I'll dock your pay.

01:32:58.377 --> 01:33:00.126
And there are people that...

01:33:01.392 --> 01:33:02.438
Lan.

01:33:03.050 --> 01:33:04.427
To your left.

01:33:08.712 --> 01:33:10.422
I know John is a good man.

01:33:10.930 --> 01:33:14.267
He's trying so hard
to mend this relationship.

01:33:15.158 --> 01:33:16.910
But sometimes,

01:33:16.935 --> 01:33:18.876
things happened,

01:33:19.646 --> 01:33:22.232
and kept us away from
falling in love again.

01:33:23.848 --> 01:33:26.725
That's when you should be strong,
and let go of each other.

01:33:27.451 --> 01:33:30.057
Give each other a chance
to meet someone...

01:33:32.116 --> 01:33:33.368
more suitable.

01:33:34.202 --> 01:33:35.870
Look at us.

01:33:36.412 --> 01:33:37.914
We've both changed.

01:33:38.584 --> 01:33:40.252
When we got together,

01:33:40.277 --> 01:33:42.321
we were just kids trying to
prove ourselves.

01:33:43.956 --> 01:33:46.334
We didn't know what we wanted.

01:33:46.636 --> 01:33:48.847
And we didn't know what
each other wanted either.

01:33:50.030 --> 01:33:51.323
Who's to blame?

01:33:53.596 --> 01:33:56.224
I want to apologize to him so much.

01:33:56.249 --> 01:33:58.043
I know I was wrong.

01:33:58.068 --> 01:33:59.650
Can I hug you?

01:34:00.728 --> 01:34:02.105
But I hope he understands.

01:34:07.527 --> 01:34:08.903
I appreciate John,

01:34:08.950 --> 01:34:10.947
for coming into my life,

01:34:11.113 --> 01:34:13.553
to teach me the lessons
of maturity.

01:34:17.880 --> 01:34:19.924
I see him as my family.

01:34:23.465 --> 01:34:25.300
And I hope...

01:34:27.964 --> 01:34:29.882
He would do the same.

01:34:40.893 --> 01:34:43.145
Somehow,

01:34:43.621 --> 01:34:45.164
this day has finally come.

01:35:40.497 --> 01:35:42.541
Everyone, they're getting married.

01:35:42.872 --> 01:35:43.998
Stop shooting!

01:35:43.998 --> 01:35:45.642
Let me introduce

01:35:45.667 --> 01:35:48.036
our bride Ngoc Nu.

01:35:51.965 --> 01:35:54.381
- And our groom Van Liem.
- Hug me!

01:35:54.406 --> 01:35:57.130
An applause for the bride and groom please!

01:36:03.363 --> 01:36:05.645
In the end, she's the only happy one,

01:36:05.687 --> 01:36:07.063
we're still lonely.

01:36:07.088 --> 01:36:09.309
We're young, we can start over.

01:36:09.457 --> 01:36:12.001
You're young, but I'm old.

01:36:12.026 --> 01:36:13.528
Are you as old as me?

01:36:13.569 --> 01:36:14.987
It's the ceremony, please be quiet.

01:36:15.029 --> 01:36:16.381
She told you to shut up.

01:36:16.406 --> 01:36:17.782
In this emotional moment,

01:36:17.782 --> 01:36:18.950
I haven't said anything...

01:36:18.975 --> 01:36:21.770
the bride must have had many things
to share with everyone.

01:36:21.911 --> 01:36:22.954
Please.

01:36:31.295 --> 01:36:32.608
You say it.

01:36:37.427 --> 01:36:38.827
Ladies and gentlemen,

01:36:39.679 --> 01:36:40.976
- toda...
- I'll do it.

01:36:41.156 --> 01:36:42.566
Let me.

01:36:48.857 --> 01:36:51.068
I used to be a selfish person.

01:36:55.027 --> 01:36:57.864
I wanted things to go my way,

01:36:58.573 --> 01:37:01.576
and I ignored the feelings
of the people around me.

01:37:03.786 --> 01:37:05.788
I do love my family,

01:37:06.622 --> 01:37:07.809
however,

01:37:08.291 --> 01:37:09.570
I loved them the wrong way.

01:37:09.769 --> 01:37:11.396
I made them sad.

01:37:12.754 --> 01:37:14.088
Can you believe that,

01:37:14.956 --> 01:37:16.332
I'm standing here,

01:37:17.341 --> 01:37:18.885
being this old,

01:37:19.260 --> 01:37:21.721
I have to learn how to love someone.

01:37:24.924 --> 01:37:25.925
Nhi!

01:37:26.642 --> 01:37:27.685
Nhu!

01:37:30.396 --> 01:37:31.564
Thank you.

01:37:33.441 --> 01:37:34.525
And...

01:37:35.771 --> 01:37:37.262
I'm sorry.

01:37:40.098 --> 01:37:42.526
My happiness,

01:37:43.367 --> 01:37:46.746
was traded by your happiness.

01:37:59.425 --> 01:38:01.803
It's getting to the good part,
stop shooting.

01:38:02.970 --> 01:38:04.096
Mom!

01:38:05.139 --> 01:38:06.808
I've never said this,

01:38:08.518 --> 01:38:09.560
but...

01:38:18.092 --> 01:38:19.301
I'm sorry.

01:38:20.647 --> 01:38:22.682
And I want you to remember that

01:38:23.074 --> 01:38:24.826
whatever happens,

01:38:25.599 --> 01:38:27.309
you'll always be my mom,

01:38:27.870 --> 01:38:29.705
and I love you.

01:38:31.332 --> 01:38:33.459
We have to be happy, okay?

01:38:33.804 --> 01:38:35.085
We will be happy.

01:38:48.933 --> 01:38:50.560
Get the wine!

01:38:50.893 --> 01:38:53.488
- Let's cheer!
- Cheers!

01:38:56.691 --> 01:38:59.193
I never thought my mom
could open her heart someday

01:38:59.193 --> 01:39:01.571
and choose to be loved again.

01:39:02.488 --> 01:39:04.282
And we can all believe that

01:39:04.407 --> 01:39:06.279
we will be able to find happiness

01:39:06.506 --> 01:39:08.341
if we choose to move forward.

01:39:09.662 --> 01:39:10.746
Nhi!

01:39:15.209 --> 01:39:16.377
Are you free tomorrow?

01:39:16.477 --> 01:39:17.520
What for?

01:39:17.545 --> 01:39:19.255
- Let's go out for dinner.
- With Lan?

01:39:19.280 --> 01:39:21.324
No, just us.

01:39:25.225 --> 01:39:26.708
You accepted it?

01:39:27.179 --> 01:39:28.890
You didn't hear it? Then forget it.

01:39:28.915 --> 01:39:30.041
No.

01:39:30.336 --> 01:39:31.649
Am I dreaming?

01:39:32.435 --> 01:39:34.123
Ouch! That hurts!

01:39:34.562 --> 01:39:35.646
It's real.

01:39:36.355 --> 01:39:37.398
Thank you!

01:39:39.586 --> 01:39:41.110
Grandma! She accepted it!

01:39:41.135 --> 01:39:44.356
She accepted it!

01:39:44.381 --> 01:39:46.258
I gave Quynh a chance,

01:39:46.782 --> 01:39:48.576
and also gave myself a chance,

01:39:48.601 --> 01:39:50.426
to keep experiencing life,

01:39:51.495 --> 01:39:52.830
and grow as a person.

01:39:53.289 --> 01:39:54.498
Just try.

01:39:54.540 --> 01:39:57.460
Each of us
only has one life to live.
